# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:17
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_00513a69:

    # "My morning alarm goes off, and I flail about uselessly for a while until I remember that I'd decided to give morning runs another shot."
    "目覚ましが鳴り出し、しばらく意味もなくごそごそと体を揺らす。やがて、今朝もランニングに挑戦すると決めていたことを思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:19
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_a01e2a23:

    # "I don't know if this was my greatest idea, but I'm determined to keep going."
    "本当にいい考えなのかどうかはわからないけど、続けると決めたんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:21
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_0dfd0461:

    # "This is about my health, after all."
    "結局、自分の健康のためなのだから。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:23
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_d09ec6f3:

    # "Sure, things haven't been great lately for me, but that hasn't made existence so intolerable that I'm not going to try everything I can to stay healthy."
    "確かに最近の俺は絶好調ってわけじゃないけど、生きるのがいやになるほどじゃない。健康でいるためにできることはなんだって試してみるさ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:25
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_0b4dd853:

    # "Besides, it's all about asserting some kind of control over this thing, right?"
    "それに、この病気を多少なりともコントロールできるようにするのが目的なんだろう？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:27
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_685ff067:

    # "If I can manage that, well, I can manage anything."
    "この体をどうにかできれば、ああ、どんなことでもなんとかやれるさ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:29
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_5fbb89f9:

    # "At least that's what I keep telling myself."
    "せめて自分自身には、そう言い聞かせ続けている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:36
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_696c0221:

    # "Once again, it would appear that I'm not alone in my run."
    "またしても、走るのは俺一人ではないらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:38
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_37bf8934:

    # "Emi has apparently been here for some time."
    "どうやら笑美はかなり前から運動場にいたようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:40
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_ed6c047c:

    # "It looks like she's already worked up a good sweat."
    "とっくにいい汗をかいているように見える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:42
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_46a55daa:

    # "Just when the hell does she come down here, anyway?"
    "というか笑美のやつ、いったい何時に運動場に来てるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:51
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_f0a7b2d7:

    # emi "Oh, it's you!"
    emi "あっ、久夫くんだぁ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:56
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_79a3ecef:

    # emi "I'm surprised to see you again!"
    emi "また久夫くんに会えたんで驚いちゃった！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:58
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_e2ba6edd:

    # hi "Why's that?"
    hi "なんで？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:63
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_f7e8bd8c:

    # emi "Well, not many people actually manage to come back for a second try."
    emi "まあ、実際にもう１回やってみようって来てくれる人は少ないってことね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:68
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_57ae5b74:

    # "She frowns, seemingly annoyed by a passing thought."
    "そんな考えに腹が立ったのか、笑美は眉をひそめる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:70
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_bb275da5:

    # emi "Like the rest of the track team, for instance."
    emi "たとえば、他の陸上部の人たちとかねー"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:72
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_58e2d097:

    # emi "Still, it was only supposed to be on a volunteer basis, so it's not that big of a shock."
    emi "でも自由参加ってことになってたから、驚くことでもないの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:74
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_dc10f30b:

    # emi "And I guess it's pretty early in the morning…"
    emi "そんで、かなり朝早いしねー"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:76
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_c20411c4:

    # "A shrug, and suddenly it appears that she's forgotten what she was talking about."
    "笑美は肩をすくめ、それでもう何を話していたか忘れたようだった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:81
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_8b64e7f1:

    # "The frown disappears entirely, and she seems to snap back to her previous train of thought."
    "不満げな表情は完全に消え失せる。さっきからの話の続きにあっさりと意識を戻したようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:83
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_272d0607:

    # emi "So! Come on, then!"
    emi "さて！　そんじゃ行こっか！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:85
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:90
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_89c01ac6:

    # emi "You're here to run again, right?"
    emi "もっかい走りにここに来たんでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:92
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_58d6697d:

    # hi "Well, yes."
    hi "まぁ、そーだな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:97
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_be090aae:

    # emi "So come on!"
    emi "それじゃ、いこ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:102
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_05c2e1e2:

    # "I find myself suddenly grabbed and yanked onto the track."
    "俺はいきなり腕を引っ張られ、競技用トラックに引きずり込まれる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:109
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_45f9a8fd:

    # "Things seem to be set on mirroring yesterday's run."
    "昨日のランニングのリピートみたいだな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:111
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_3809c0d7:

    # "That is, I seem to be struggling, while Emi moves with an effortlessness that I find enviable."
    "つまり、俺は必死なのに、笑美は羨ましいほど余裕で走っているってことだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:113
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_ef1c6029:

    # "It's incredibly bothersome, to be so easily worn out."
    "こんなにあっさりくたびれてしまうなんて、ひどく腹立たしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:115
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_50f70fe4:

    # "I know I should be patient, work toward things gradually, but…"
    "我慢して、地道に頑張らなきゃいけないってことはわかってる、けど……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:117
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_5d4f7a25:

    # "It's difficult to stay positive about this."
    "前向きな気持ちを保つのは難しい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:119
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_9f1332f3:

    # "We round the track and start on our second lap."
    "俺たちはトラックを１周し、２周目に入る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:123
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_fbef6d4c:

    # "Emi seems to have grown impatient keeping pace with me, and begins to pull away."
    "笑美は俺のペースに合わせるのに飽きたのか、俺を引き離し始める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:125
translate jp a1_friday_exercise_1fe80443:

    # "This is where I gave out yesterday."
    "俺は昨日、ここでへたばったんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:158
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_949ead76:

    # "I wake up and take a hot shower."
    "起床後、熱いシャワーを浴びる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:163
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_797e8cf3:

    # "Back in my room, the first thing I see is the familiar row of medication bottles lined up on top of my dresser, and it makes me depressed, as usual."
    "部屋に戻ると、最初に目に入るのはおなじみ机の上の薬瓶の列。いつものことだけど憂鬱になる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:165
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_45b40751:

    # "It's annoying. I thought I was okay. I thought I had made my peace with this thing, gotten over it."
    "不愉快だ。大丈夫だと思っていた。もう折り合いをつけたつもりだった。乗り越えたつもりだった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:167
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_9a0611ca:

    # "But what I really did… I allowed myself to forget that I have a problem. Being here really reminds me of the reality, and trying to fight against it just hurts."
    "でも実際は……自分が病気を抱えているということから逃避していただけだ。ここにいると現実を思い知らされる。現実と戦うのが辛くて仕方ない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:169
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_135776b0:

    # "Reflecting on it is only going to do so much. I've done this before, for months. It seems like it's time to get over it."
    "くよくよ悩んでいたって解決しない。前もそうだった。何ヶ月も。もう立ち直る時だろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:171
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_2ff912b6:

    # "If I allow myself to forget that my life is definitely not going to be as long as those of others, I won't get anywhere."
    "他の人のようにはまず長生きできないという事実から逃避していても、何も得られない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:173
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_73a1ed91:

    # "My life may be different from others. But it is a life in progress."
    "俺の人生は、他の人とは違うかもしれない。でもこの人生は現在進行中なんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:175
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_24456c72:

    # "That is how I'll rationalize it."
    "そう思って納得しよう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:177
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_f030ccb4:

    # "I down the usual handful of pills, trying to push the sudden dreary feeling out of my head. Then I prepare to head out to class early, as usual."
    "この突然沸きあがったつまらない気分を追い出すように、いつもと同じ一握りの錠剤を飲む。早めに家を出るよう準備する。これもいつも通り。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:182
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_88fcf46c:

    # "As I step into the hallway, I notice Kenji coming around the hallway corner, stealthily making his way over to his own room with a large bag. As he sneaks past me soundlessly like a ninja hiding in plain sight, I call out to him."
    "廊下に出ると、廊下の角からこちらへ歩いてくる健二を発見する。大きなかばんを抱えて忍ぶように部屋に向かっている。景色に溶け込む忍者のように音もなく俺の横を通り過ぎようとするそいつに、俺は声をかける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:184
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_20a67d9a:

    # hi "Hey."
    hi "よう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:191
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_b33550f5:

    # "He jumps at the sound of my voice."
    "俺の声に飛び上がる健二。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:193
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_1b216d6a:

    # ke "Oh, hey, man. I didn't notice you there. I'm really tired."
    ke "ああ……なんだよ、気づかなかったよ。マジ疲れてるんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:195
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_a5094f1a:

    # "I think it's more like he didn't see me, but that's not the issue."
    "見えなかったと言ったほうが正しいんじゃないだろうか？　ってそんなことよりも、"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:197
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_12b829d1:

    # hi "Where have you been this early? Shopping?"
    hi "こんな早くからどこ行ってたんだ？　買い物？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:202
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_0dfd291c:

    # ke "Nah, I wasn't shopping. Sometimes I have to visit… the math teacher. Yeah, I figured it would be a good idea to find out when the next exam is, since he tells you in advance if you want."
    ke "いや、買い物じゃねえよ。時々……数学教師に会いに行かないといけないんだ。ああ、次の試験日を聞いておくのもいいと思ったし。あいつは聞けば事前に教えてくれるからな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:204
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_f17bb445:

    # hi "So then, what's in the bag?"
    hi "じゃあ、そのかばんの中には何が？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:209
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_5c9c638c:

    # ke "I thought I'd go shopping while I was outside. I need supplies to continue the fight against the vast feminist conspiracy."
    ke "外に出たついでに買い物しようと思ってな。フェミニストの巨大な陰謀と戦い続けるには、物資が必要なんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:211
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_c5dda460:

    # hi "Uh, okay."
    hi "ああ……そうか"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:213
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_673e1ad5:

    # hi "I thought you didn't go outside."
    hi "お前、外には出ないんじゃなかったのか"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:218
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_40caa75f:

    # ke "I wear a hat now."
    ke "帽子をかぶるようにしたからな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:220
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_8285e573:

    # "I decide to not point out that he is not wearing a hat."
    "帽子なんて見当たらないけど放っておこう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:222
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_18ab6249:

    # "An awkward silence settles between us and then Kenji breaks it by pushing his door open slowly, releasing a creaking sound into the air that only makes the moment seem more awkward. He sets the bag down inside his room and then closes the door."
    "俺たちの間に気まずい沈黙が漂う。健二がゆっくりと部屋のドアを開くと、ギイギイと音がして余計に気まずくなる。健二はかばんを中に置いてドアを閉める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:224
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_7fb638a1:

    # hi "I'm surprised you went out of your way to find out a test date. Trying to take advantage of an opportunity to study is pretty diligent."
    hi "わざわざテストの日程を調べに行くとは驚いたよ。前もって予習しておくなんて、けっこう真面目なんだな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:229
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_14988636:

    # ke "I never study."
    ke "勉強なんかしねえよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:231
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_f0fc03db:

    # hi "Oh…"
    hi "はあ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:236
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_c0148a9d:

    # ke "I just wanted to know when the next test day was. I'm still going to take it, duh. I need to know so I know what day I can't afford to skip class. He usually sends out updates on that crap by phone, so I had to step out and check up on it."
    ke "次のテストの日が知りたかっただけだ。それでもテストは受けるんだぜ。当たり前だろ。授業をサボれない日を知る為に聞きにいったんだ あいつはあのクソテストの日程を電話で伝えてくるんだ。だから外に出て調べないといけなかったんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:238
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_9a95cb38:

    # hi "And why do you have to go out, when you can get it on your phone?"
    hi "なんで外に行かないといけないんだ、電話で済むのに？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:243
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_ab6f8fd8:

    # ke "I don't carry a phone."
    ke "俺、電話は持ち歩かないんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:245
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_0fec17a5:

    # hi "What do you mean you don't carry a phone? You mean you just leave it at home?"
    hi "持ち歩かないって？　部屋に置いてるってこと？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:250
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_a9f1eca9:

    # ke "Nah, I don't use phones. I don't have a phone. Phones. I have no phone."
    ke "ちげえよ、俺は電話は使わないんだ。持ってないんだよ、電話。一つも持ってない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:252
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_fd2f312b:

    # hi "Why don't you have a phone? How can you not have a phone? No phone at all? No phone?"
    hi "なんで持ってないんだ？　電話持ってないなんて、そんなわけあるかよ？　一つもないのか？　電話なしか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:257
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_42e68966:

    # ke "I just don't like phones. Actually, I'm kind of scared of them. I don't know why. I think it's some kind of repressed trauma."
    ke "電話は嫌いなんだよ。なんか怖いし。上手く説明できないけど。抑圧されたトラウマってやつかもな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:259
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_454df66d:

    # ke "But, basically, when I hear a phone, I get nervous. It's my darkest secret."
    ke "まあ要するに、電話の音を聞くと不安になるんだ。俺の一番の秘密な"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:264
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_1fc5b5b8:

    # ke "I have two theories on it: either I have some fear of receiving some undefined, ominous, life-altering doom call, or I was beaten with a phone in the past. Beaten so badly I can't remember it."
    ke "原因は二つ考えられる。誰からともなく、俺の人生を変えるような、不気味な悪夢の電話がかかってくるのを恐れているのか さもなきゃ昔電話で殴られたことがあるか、だ。思い出せないくらいひどく殴られたんだろうな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:266
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_293199d9:

    # hi "Beaten in the head."
    hi "頭を叩かれたんだろうな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:271
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_29e066d6:

    # ke "Well, where else could I get beaten with a phone that would make me unable to remember it? The ass?"
    ke "他にどこ叩かれたら思い出せなくなるっていうんだよ。ケツ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:273
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_48fe34d7:

    # "Unexpectedly logical. I feel very depressed now. Sensing this conversation is more or less over, Kenji opens his door again and prepares to head inside."
    "意外なほど論理的な答えが返ってくる。なんかすごく気が滅入る。会話も終わりだと判断して、健二はまたドアを開けて中に入ろうとする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:278
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_98e4eb80:

    # ke "Yeah, I'm going to sleep, dude. Have a good one."
    ke "さて寝るとするか。お前もがんばれよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:280
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_eddb6816:

    # hi "Class is going to start in like twenty minutes."
    hi "あと２０分ぐらいで授業始まるんだが"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:285
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_0c850f76:

    # ke "I already did something today. Too tired to go to school."
    ke "もう今日は頑張ったからな。くたくたで学校行けない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:290
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_86936fff:

    # ke "Hey, you need some lip balm? I accidentally bought two because I thought the store had started selling individual double A batteries."
    ke "そうだ、リップクリームいらないか？　単三電池をバラ売りし始めたのかと思って間違って二つも買っちまったんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:292
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_a693bd2d:

    # hi "Thanks but no thanks."
    hi "どーも、でもいらない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:298
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_e5fdb6b1:

    # ke "Whatever, man."
    ke "はいはいそうかよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:305
translate jp a1_friday_invisible_hat_32bcfe94:

    # "He swiftly enters his lair, finally letting me go to the class."
    "健二がそそくさと自分の部屋へ戻ったので、俺もようやく学校へ向かえる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:322
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_5e32ce75:

    # "The door down the hall opens with a crack as it swings forward from being pushed opened too strongly and crashing against the wall. The sound is followed by a peal of bubbly laughter, and I instantly know who it is."
    "廊下の先にあるドアが勢いよく開かれて、壁にぶつかってばぐんと大きな音を立てる。続いて陽気な大笑いがこっちまで響いてくる。声の主は一発でわかる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:343
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_155d6bb6:

    # "At the noise, Kenji disappears into his room like a ninja, slamming the door shut just as Shizune and Misha walk over, the former taking small, efficient steps towards me while the latter more or less bounces off the walls."
    "音を聞いたとたん、健二は忍者のように自分の部屋へと消える。ドアがぴしゃりと閉まるのと同時に、静音とミーシャがやってくる。 静音はきびきびと素早い足取りで、一方ミーシャはほとんど壁の間を跳ね回っているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:348
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_e47f96c5:

    # "I try to do the same as Kenji, but it's too late. Misha puts her foot between my door to prevent me closing it, so I have no other choice but to let them in."
    "健二を見習って部屋に逃げようとするけど、遅かった。ドアを閉められないようミーシャが足を突っ込んできたので、二人を中に入れるしかなくなる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:356
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:364
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_5919b973:

    # mi "Hi, Hicchan~! Hi~ hi~!"
    mi "おはよ、ひっちゃん～！　おはよ～おはよ～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:366
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_ca61152d:

    # hi "Hi."
    hi "よう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:368
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_96e7cced:

    # hi "What are you two doing here?"
    hi "二人ともこんなところで何してる？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:370
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_c53c317a:

    # "I wonder if the pause between those two sentences was politely long enough."
    "邪険に聞こえないよう、言葉の間にはじゅうぶん間を空けたつもりだけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:375
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:380
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_13d62cd5:

    # mi "Hicchan, that's rude~! We came to pick you up!"
    mi "ひっちゃん失礼だよ～！　わたしたち迎えに来てあげたんだよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:385
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_82463158:

    # mi "Did you think we thought you were going to escape and came to make sure you didn't? Surely not, Hicchan~!"
    mi "ひっちゃんが逃げるかもしれないから、逃げないように捕まえておこうとしてると思ったの？　そんなわけないじゃ～ん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:387
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_c169577a:

    # hi "Hey, I didn't say that that's what you were here for."
    hi "ちょっと待てよ、それがお前らの目的だなんて言ってないだろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:389
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_64690b9c:

    # "But now I know it's exactly what they are here for."
    "でもそれが二人の目的だってことはもう明らかだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:394
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_360545a9:

    # mi "It's time for student council work, yes it is~!"
    mi "ほらほら、生徒会の仕事する時間だよ～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:399
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_41f61d7a:

    # mi "Aren't you happy, Hicchan, to be able to help the whole~ school~! You are like, a hero~! The future generations will tell stories of this day!"
    mi "ひっちゃん、ついに学校全体のお手伝いができるんだよ～！　うれしいでしょ～？　ヒーローみたいだよ～！　今日という日はきっと子々孫々の代まで語り継がれるよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:401
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_ddd0bd94:

    # "Interesting. I didn't think joining the Student Council would be a heroic deed worthy of Hercules."
    "おもしろいな。生徒会に入るのがヘラクレスなみに英雄的な行為だとは思わなかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:403
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_a18fdc70:

    # hi "Well… I guess I did promise so…"
    hi "いやまあ……確かに約束はしたけどさ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:410
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_2a3a5310:

    # "I've neglected Shizune, and only now do I notice her in the corner of my vision, peering around my room over my shoulder, her analytical eyes darting from object to object…"
    "ほったらかしにしていた静音が、俺の視野の端に入ってくる。あいつは俺の肩越しに部屋の中を見渡している。あの分析するような目で、じろじろ視線を移しながら……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:412
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_b8ed9f30:

    # "This is kinda intrusive, the feeling of being exposed crawls in my balls. Luckily I don't have dirty laundry on the floor or anything like that."
    "人の部屋に勝手に入って何してるんだ。裸を見られたような感覚にタマがむずむずする。幸い、脱いだ服やらなんやらが床に散らかっていたりはしないけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:417
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:422
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_b2b9f396:

    # mi "Hm~? What is it, Shicchan?"
    mi "ん～？　どしたの、しっちゃん？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:427
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_d752cf94:

    # mi "Yeah, this is Hicchan's room~! We haven't seen it before, I didn't even realize!"
    mi "そうだよ、ここはひっちゃんの部屋～！　そういえば今まで来たことなかったよね！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:432
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_b5ece7ee:

    # mi "It's kinda plain, but Hicchan hasn't had time to decorate it yet, isn't that so~?"
    mi "なんだか地味だけど、ひっちゃんまだ飾り付けする時間がなかったんだよね～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:437
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_359cdcba:

    # mi "What are those?"
    mi "それな～に？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:439
translate jp a1_friday_home_field_advantage_07d47612:

    # "She points at my collection of medications on the night table."
    "ミーシャはナイトテーブルの上に並んだ、薬瓶の数々を指さす。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:466
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_d0650c63:

    # "The halls are quiet as the courtyard was, naturally so since everyone is in class. I knock lightly at the door of 3-3 and push open the door when Mutou calls from the other side."
    "廊下は中庭と同じように静かだ。みんな授業に出ているから当たり前だけど。３年３組のドアを軽くノックして、武藤先生が呼び入れるのを聞いてドアを開く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:471
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_8969d572:

    # hi "Sorry I'm late."
    hi "遅れてすみません"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:473
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_61ea9f25:

    # "Fifteen pairs of eyes turn to me."
    "１５組の目が俺のほうを向く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:478
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_1b8b00bb:

    # mu "Good morning, Nakai."
    mu "おはよう、中井"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:480
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_808004e5:

    # "Mutou seems to be somewhat confounded by my coming in late, as if I interrupted his flow or something."
    "武藤先生は俺が遅れて入ってきたせいで面食らっているようだ。何か授業の流れを邪魔してしまったんだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:482
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_d02a4525:

    # "Judging from the rambling lectures his classes tend to be, that might be the case."
    "いつもとりとめのない授業をしていることを考えれば、それが正解なのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:484
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_e6f7adcd:

    # "I pass him the note the nurse gave me. Mutou takes it with a nod and reads it quickly."
    "ナースにもらったメモを先生に渡す。先生はうなずいてそれに素早く目を通す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:489
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_104e2518:

    # "He lifts his eyebrows and gives me a kind of a stern look but doesn't say anything, just nods solemnly again."
    "先生は眉を上げると険しい目で俺を見る。でも何も言わず、ただもう一度重々しくうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:491
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_ffe8ed3c:

    # "I shrug and he gestures at me to run along so I naturally do."
    "俺は肩をすくめる。先生に席に着けと無言で促され、俺はそのまま従う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:497
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_cee861ca:

    # "For a change, I'm not among the first ones to come to morning class."
    "昨日までと違って、俺は教室に入るのが遅いほうだった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:499
translate jp a1_friday_no_recovery_ce3bc0ba:

    # "Instead, almost everyone else seems to be here already. I recognize most of my class by their faces by now, though the names escape me still."
    "逆に、ほとんどクラスの全員がすでに来ているみたいだ。もうクラスメイトの顔はほとんど見分けが付く。名前はまだ覚えてないけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:511
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_ad370459:

    # "Only two pairs of eyes remain keenly following me as I walk to my seat."
    "俺が席に着く間、２組の視線だけが俺をしっかりと捕らえつづける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:513
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_781dddbf:

    # "I'm not surprised in the least when I feel Misha's fingernail prickle through my shirt about fifteen seconds after seating myself."
    "席に着いてから１５秒ほど後、ミーシャの爪が俺のシャツをつつくのを感じる。俺は驚きもしない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:525
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_8c3bcc6a:

    # mi "Psst! Where were you?"
    mi "ねえねえ！　どこに行ってたの？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:527
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_f25ed1db:

    # hi "None of your business."
    hi "お前には関係ない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:529
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_4c1335d3:

    # "I know this is probably the worst answer I can give as it only serves to pique their curiosity, but I have no energy to come up with elaborate cover stories right now."
    "これが一番まずい答え方なのはわかっている。これじゃ二人の好奇心をかき立てるだけだ。でも手の込んだ作り話を思いつくような気力は今の俺にはない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:538
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_dbece9fa:

    # "However, Misha backs off. She's unexpectedly fast to give up today."
    "でもミーシャは引き下がる。今日はずいぶんあっさりあきらめるな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:540
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:542
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_fefd9f0f:

    # "In a minute, she's back at poking me with her finger."
    "でもすぐに、ミーシャがまた指でつついてくる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:549
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_722c6020:

    # mi "Come on, tell us! Shicchan is very interested too!"
    mi "いいじゃん、教えてよ！　しっちゃんもすごく知りたいって！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:551
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_e97dd7cb:

    # "It was just my wishful thinking. She just talked about it with Shizune, probably devising ways to get me to spill the beans."
    "俺が甘かった。ミーシャは静音に話していただけだったんだ。どうやって俺に吐かせようかと相談していたんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:553
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_7efcef0d:

    # hi "No."
    hi "だめだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:562
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_7beecdc7:

    # "She retreats to negotiate again."
    "ミーシャはまた引っこんで相談する。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:573
translate jp a1_friday_slow_recovery_fdd7191d:

    # mi "As a member of the Student Council, it's your duty to tell us why you are skipping class! Especially if it's something fun fun fun~!" nointeract
    mi "生徒会の一員として、授業をさぼった理由は正直に話さなきゃダメだよ！　それがお楽しみだったらなおさらね～！" nointeract

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:607
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_6fe024fa:

    # "Once inside the office, I look around and see that it's deserted."
    "生徒会室に入って中を見渡すと、誰もいなかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:609
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_041ede26:

    # hi "I guess this means there isn't a lot of work left, huh? Since there's no one here, and all."
    hi "あんまり仕事は残ってないみたいだな？　ほかに誰もいないみたいだし"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:614
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_cc51e8a8:

    # mi "It's always like this, Hicchan~!"
    mi "ここはいつもこんな感じだよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:616
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_989b9e30:

    # "This confirms what I have thought before but have never actually been able to confirm definitively: Shizune and Misha are the Student Council. The whole Student Council."
    "前から思っていたけど、今まではっきりとは確かめられなかったことが今はっきりした。静音とミーシャこそが生徒会なんだ。これで全部、他には誰もいないんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:618
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_d72dec0d:

    # hi "Damn. So it's true. The Student Council is really only you two."
    hi "くっそ、やっぱりそうだったんだな。生徒会には本当にお前ら二人しかいないんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:626
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_48a4d265:

    # "Shizune looks as if she's stuck wondering whether to be ashamed or explode with anger, and Misha is equally divided between laughing and trying to stop her."
    "静音は恥じるべきか怒りで爆発するべきか迷っているように見える。ミーシャも笑おうか静音を止めようかと、同じくらい迷っているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:631
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:636
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_476088df:

    # mi "Well, then, Hicchan, you'll be happy to know that since it's just us three, we have a lot to do! A lot~! A lot~ lot~ lot~…"
    mi "じゃあひっちゃん、喜んでちょうだい。わたしたち三人しかいないんだから、やることはいっぱいあるのよ！ いっぱい～！　いっぱい～いっぱい～いっぱい～……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:638
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_db149d8d:

    # hi "That does not make me happy."
    hi "全然嬉しくないぞ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:643
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_295e631b:

    # "But it seems to make Shizune very happy."
    "でも静音は大いに嬉しそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:648
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_e39fcd2d:

    # mi "Wahaha~!"
    mi "わはは～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:653
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_1089b6dc:

    # mi "Just kidding!"
    mi "冗談だよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:659
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_3cf5cff1:

    # "The work turns out to be sorting and double-checking the considerable amount of paperwork necessary for an event such as the school festival to get done."
    "仕事というのは書類の仕分けと再チェックだった。学園祭のような大きなイベントに必要な書類の量は、膨大なものだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:661
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_0c004e2f:

    # "Bureaucracy is a mindboggling thing."
    "事務の仕事ってのは気が遠くなるな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:665
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_699b5e34:

    # "But we manage to finish it just when the lunch bells ring."
    "それでも、昼のチャイムが鳴る前になんとか片づける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:671
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_cbff0d17:

    # mi "Okay~, now that we are done, we can relax a little! But not too much, we have lots more to do in the afternoon~!"
    mi "おっけ～、仕事も済んだし、少し休めるよ！　でもあんまりゆっくりはできないよ、午後にはもっとたくさんあるからね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:678
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:683
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_f845ed04:

    # mi "It's actually not that much work, Hicchan~. So~, we can afford to enjoy a little lunch first."
    mi "ほんとはそんなにいっぱいでもないよ、ひっちゃん～。だから～、先にお昼食べる時間はあるよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:688
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_66b999fb:

    # mi "Hahaha~!"
    mi "ははは～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:690
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_8dcf6e64:

    # "The two of them produce a small array of plastic containers seemingly out of thin air."
    "どこからともなく、二人はプラスチックの容器を一式取り出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:695
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_482868ae:

    # mi "Hm~ hm~… It's chicken cutlet with tomatoes and soybean sprouts~! Doesn't it sound delicious, Hicchan?"
    mi "ふむふむ～……チキンカツと、つけあわせにトマトともやしだよ～！　もう聞いただけでおいしそうだよね、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:697
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_f32d2d9f:

    # mi "It was just made this morning, and it's still warm, so eat eat eat~!"
    mi "今朝作ったばっかりだし、まだ温かいから、食べて食べて食べて～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:699
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_01b801ff:

    # "I take one of the containers and open it. It looks nice, and certainly smells good. The fact that I'm really hungry adds to that even more."
    "俺は容器を一つ取り上げて開いてみる。見た目もいいし、おいしそうな匂いがする。とても腹が減っているので、余計にそう感じる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:701
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_1d9c61b4:

    # hi "Wow, this looks great. Where did you get this?"
    hi "おー、すごくおいしそうだな。どこで買ってきたんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:706
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:711
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_6bbf8327:

    # mi "That isn't important, Hicchan!"
    mi "そんなのどうでもいいでしょ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:716
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_1625d11f:

    # mi "There was supposed to be a stall selling lunchboxes, but the girl who was to run it suddenly said she couldn't do it. Shicchan said, 'What a waste, it was a lot of work to trick Hicchan into making this~'—"
    mi "お弁当の屋台を出すはずだったんだけど、担当の子が急にできないって言いだしたの。しっちゃんは『ひっちゃんをだましてこれ作らせるのにすごく苦労したのに、無駄になっちゃった～』って――"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:718
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_733030a0:

    # hi "Hey, what the hell…"
    hi "おい、なんだって……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:723
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_639bcfab:

    # mi "…So~! Shicchan wanted to see if she could do it, but then decided not to, right, Shicchan~?"
    mi "……それで～！　しっちゃんは自分でできるか試してみたけど、結局やめることにしたの。ね、しっちゃん～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:728
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_6a7946ec:

    # "Shizune sulks angrily, shooting Misha a displeased look. I don't think I was supposed to hear that story."
    "静音は腹立たしげにすねてしまい、ミーシャを不満そうににらみつける。今の話は俺が聞いたらまずかったんじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:730
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_4b15d35f:

    # hi "This is your test food?"
    hi "この弁当は実験ってことか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:735
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:740
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_7f760716:

    # mi "I'm eating it too, Hicchan~!"
    mi "わたしも食べるよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:745
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_d82675a0:

    # mi "And Shicchan is, too~!"
    mi "しっちゃんもね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:747
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_a3ba4b25:

    # "That doesn't answer the question!"
    "答えになってないだろ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:749
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_294a409d:

    # "Nevertheless, I split a pair of chopsticks Shizune offers me, pick up a piece of cutlet, and pop it into my mouth."
    "それでも、俺は静音がくれた箸を割ってチキンカツを一切れつまみ、口に放り込む。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:751
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_a0b1bb10:

    # hi "It's surprisingly good. I didn't expect Shizune to be such a good cook."
    hi "すごくおいしいじゃん。驚いたよ。静音がこんなに料理が上手だなんて思わなかった"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:756
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_b79cae73:

    # "Shizune puts her chopsticks down to sign curtly towards Misha, who gulps down her cutlet with noticeable difficulty in order to speak for her."
    "静音が箸をおいて、そっけなくミーシャに手話する。ミーシャは通訳しようとして、食べていたチキンカツをとても難儀そうに飲みこむ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:761
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_95e89266:

    # mi "Hicchan~! Don't talk with food in your mouth~!"
    mi "ひっちゃん～！　口に食べ物を入れたまましゃべらないの～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:763
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_2a3eb637:

    # hi "It's not like I enjoy doing it. Anyway, how motherly to show that kind of concern…"
    hi "別に好きでやってるわけじゃないぞ。ていうか、母親みたいなこと言うよな……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:768
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:773
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_0f74a283:

    # mi "You can't even eat right, Hicchan~! That's all it is~!"
    mi "あなたは食事もまともにできないってことよ、ひっちゃん～！　それだけ～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:778
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_9ecd4c2d:

    # "It's a stalemate. I can't eat in order to talk to Shizune, who can't eat in order to chastise me for eating the wrong way. Misha, caught in between, is in the same situation, and looks the most disheartened by how this is going."
    "膠着状態だ。俺は静音と話そうとすれば食事ができないし、静音は俺の食べ方が行儀悪いとガミガミ叱るので食事ができない。 間に挟まれたミーシャも同じ状態で、ことの成り行きに一番がっかりしているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:784
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_649555d8:

    # "Either way, our food is getting colder by the second, and it wasn't piping hot to start with. Wherever this was going, it dies down pretty fast once we all realize that, and we eat."
    "どちらにしても、もともと熱々だったわけでもない食事はどんどん冷めていく。結論はともかく、そのことに気づいた俺たちはさっさと話をやめにして、食事にありつく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:788
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_4c45c996:

    # "After a while the bell rings, but Misha makes no attempt to tell Shizune, so I'm sure they're planning to skip classes and spend the rest of the day in here again."
    "しばらくしてチャイムが鳴る。でもミーシャは静音に伝えようともしない。また授業をさぼって一日ここで過ごす気なんだろう。間違いない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:793
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:798
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_8bbe86f5:

    # mi "Hicchan, do you have any plans for the festival?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、学園祭は何か予定ある？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:800
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_46ecdf4d:

    # hi "No, not really. After all, I've only been here a week, what could I set up in that time?"
    hi "いや、特にはないよ。もともと転校して一週間しかたってないんだし、そんなにすぐに予定なんて立てられるわけないし"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:805
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_67d5e709:

    # mi "Wahaha~! Hicchan, you helped us out so much, don't sell yourself short!"
    mi "わはは～！　ひっちゃん、いっぱい手伝ってくれたじゃない。あんまり自分を安売りしちゃだめだよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:807
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "わかったよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:812
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:817
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_28a869e4:

    # mi "We're serious~!"
    mi "本気で言ってるんだから～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:819
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_112d0f20:

    # hi "Okay!"
    hi "わかったってば！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:821
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_076e571c:

    # "The two of them seem to get indignant over the strangest things."
    "二人とも、ほんとにおかしなことに怒りだすな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:826
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_7:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:831
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_87002722:

    # mi "You're going though, right, Hicchan? You should at least see what we've ac—complished…? Everyone should be able to look at what they have done so they can fully understand their work, that's my belief~! You're no exception!"
    mi "学園祭には行くんだよね、ひっちゃん？　少なくともわたしたちが、どれだけのことをじょう……じゅ……？　したのか、見ておくべきよ 誰だって、自分の仕事の成果を見て、それをちゃんと理解するべきよ！　それがわたしの信念なの～！　ひっちゃんも例外じゃないわよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:836
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_77edb534:

    # mi "Hicchan, you should definitely go~! If you don't have anything planned, then maybe we can even go together~!"
    mi "ひっちゃん、絶対行ったほうがいいよ～！　ほかに予定がないなら、わたしたちも一緒につきあってもいいよ～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:841
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_8518220f:

    # hi "Do you need a hand? If there's anything you need help with, I'm fine with sticking around."
    hi "ほかに何か手伝うことはないか？　助けがいるなら、しばらくここにいても構わないけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:843
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_757ac1a0:

    # "I feel much more at ease than I did earlier; my previous concerns and fears long gone. I'd forgotten about this morning's trouble entirely until now, having fun with Shizune like this."
    "さっきよりもずっと気分が楽になっている。心配ごとや恐れもとっくになくなっている。静音と楽しく過ごしていたら、今朝のトラブルのことも今のいままですっかり忘れていた。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:845
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_cc11453c:

    # "Having fun with Shizune… It seems like an unfamiliar concept to think of, but, looking back on it, I've really enjoyed the moments I've spent with Shizune and Misha these past few days, in spite of everything else."
    "静音と楽しく……いまいちしっくりこない考え方だ。でも思い返せば、この数日間静音とミーシャと一緒に過ごした時間は本当に楽しかった。まあそうでないこともあったけど、それでも。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:847
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_56daf2ce:

    # "If we might be going together, then maybe I can afford to stick around a little longer. And I guess it beats class."
    "一緒に学園祭に行くんだったら、もう少しここにいたっていいか。授業に行くよりはよっぽどいいだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:852
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_8:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:857
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_08dd915c:

    # mi "Really, Hicchan? Okay~! We can consider this you repaying us for the free lunch~!"
    mi "ほんとに、ひっちゃん？　おっけ～！　じゃあその分でお弁当のおごりのお返しってことにしておくね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:862
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_fd8db1cb:

    # mi "Great, this is great, really~ really~ great~! Shicchan was hoping to bring this up again later anyway! Ahahaha~! Wahahahahaha~!"
    mi "いいね、すごくいいね、すっごくすっごくいいね～！　どっちみちしっちゃんは後で仕事頼むつもりだったんだけどね！　あははは～！　わははははは～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:864
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_dd41e4e2:

    # "That's not a free lunch at all. Normally I would be angry, or at least slightly unsettled, but my mood has improved from earlier on, so I'll let it slide."
    "それはおごりとは全然言わないだろう。普段なら俺は怒るか、少なくともちょっとは動揺したと思う。でも今までよりは気分が良くなっているので、俺は突っ込まないことにする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:866
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_e63b4297:

    # "Helping them out turns out to consist mostly of stamping forms and making what seems like ten thousand copies apiece of fifty different budget reports."
    "手伝いというのは、書類にはんこを押したり、５０種類の予算計画書をそれぞれ１００００部コピーするような仕事がほとんどだった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:868
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_3414caa4:

    # "It's not hard, but very boring, and according to Misha, the simplest of the tasks they deal with."
    "難しくはないけど非常に退屈だ。しかもミーシャによれば、二人の仕事の中でも一番単純なほうらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:870
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_10bec7da:

    # "I feel myself getting more and more tired, and with that, less eager to return to class. This is especially bad because the more time I spend out of class, the harder it seems to just get up and go back."
    "どんどん疲労がたまっていき、同時に授業に戻る意欲が失われていく。さぼっている時間が長引くほど、立ち上がって教室に戻るのが難しくなるわけで、これは実にまずい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:872
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_3a032652:

    # "These two, they're a terrible influence. Terrible role models. Not that it bothers me all that much, and I'm sure no one looks up to them, but it's the principle of the thing…"
    "こいつら、本当にろくでもないお手本だな。悪い影響を与えまくりだ。別に俺が心配してるってわけじゃないし、生徒から尊敬されてるとも思えないけど、世の中って往々にしてそんなものか……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:877
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_9:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:882
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_dff1662f:

    # mi "Done~!"
    mi "おわり～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:884
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_773fbdd8:

    # hi "Ah, that was fast. I'll be finished before this period's over, I think."
    hi "お、ずいぶん早いじゃん。こっちは次の授業が始まるまでには終わると思う"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:889
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_87f7d968:

    # mi "No, no, Hicchan, everything is done. So, you're done, too~!"
    mi "ちがうちがう、ひっちゃん、もう全部片づいたの。だからひっちゃんもおつかれさま～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:891
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_01e7a9f8:

    # hi "That doesn't make any sense, are you telling me this is all arbitrary and you've been keeping me here for the hell of it?"
    hi "全然訳わからないぞ。じゃあ仕事ってのは全部適当で、ただ意味もなく俺を引き留めてたってことか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:896
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_e364bd58:

    # mi "No~…"
    mi "ちがうよ～……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:901
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_10:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:906
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ed73729f:

    # mi "But we have kept you long enough~! You should go back to class, Hicchan~! You can still make it for most of this period!"
    mi "でも長く引き留め過ぎちゃったね～！　もう授業に戻ったほうがいいわ、ひっちゃん～！　今ならまだ、残りの授業に十分間に合うよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:908
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_0583026f:

    # hi "What about you?"
    hi "お前らはどうするんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:913
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_ef2b123c_11:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:918
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_50eeaf9d:

    # mi "Of course we're coming too, of course; we'll be right behind you!"
    mi "もちろん行くわよもちろん。すぐについていくから！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:925
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_74ae9353:

    # "Reassured, I start heading back to class, but the period is almost halfway over, so I start thinking it would be pointless halfway there and pass the difference between this class and the next drinking juice in the hallway."
    "安心して、俺は教室に戻ろうとする。でも授業はだいたい半分くらい過ぎていたし、あまり戻る意味もない気がしてくる。なので、廊下でジュースを飲みながら次の授業まで暇をつぶすことにする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:927
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_0624e4c3:

    # "I keep an eye on the door to the student council room, but it doesn't open. What's taking them so long? Are they busy wrapping up my share of the work? Well, it shouldn't take so long, unless there's more, and they just wanted me to leave."
    "生徒会室のドアをしばらく眺めてみるけど、ドアは開かない。どうしてこんなに時間がかかるんだ？　俺がやっていた作業を仕上げるのに忙しいのか？ まあ、それならそんなに時間がかかるはずはない。まだ仕事が残っていて、単に俺に出て行ってほしかった、ということでなければ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:929
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_65c7457b:

    # "The more I think about it, the likelier it seems."
    "考えれば考えるほど、そんな気がしてくる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:931
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_bdcf585f:

    # "Shizune is… well, not an idiot, but clearly, she's unable to just come out with things."
    "静音は……まあ、バカではないけど、でも不器用なところがあるよな。明らかに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:933
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_d190b67e:

    # "Maybe it's because she can't talk, so it's harder for her. She has Misha, but all in all, as easy as they make it look, there's still a difference between casual speech and sign language."
    "話ができないから、そういうのが難しい、ということなのかもしれない。静音にはミーシャがいるけど、それがどんなに簡単そうに見えても、通訳のいらない会話と手話の間にはやっぱり違いはある。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:937
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_a686e8fb:

    # "I contemplate going back there to check on them, but the bell rings, and I have to go to class."
    "戻って二人の様子を確かめてみようか、と考える。でもチャイムが鳴ってしまったので、俺は教室に戻らないといけない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:942
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_c85a6f52:

    # "They join me a few minutes later, and the thoughts I had in my mind before slip away in the routine of school life."
    "数分後に、二人とも教室に入ってくる。さっきの考えごとも、平凡な学校生活にまぎれてすっかり忘れてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:946
translate jp a1_friday_no_free_lunch_890bcbf6:

    # "By the time I remember, school is over for the day and I'm too tired to do anything but go home, do my homework, and then go to sleep."
    "ふと気がつけば、とっくに一日の授業は終わっていた。疲れはてた俺は部屋に戻って、宿題をやって寝るくらいしかできない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:963
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f7788298:

    # "Normally, I'd join the flow and grab a lunch myself, but today is different."
    "いつもなら人の流れに乗って食堂に行き、一人でさっさと昼飯を食べるところだけど、今日は違う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:965
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f214a940:

    # "Today, I've been invited to lunch on the roof."
    "今日は屋上でのランチに招待されている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:967
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a61daa64:

    # "An odd location, but that's where I was told to go."
    "おかしな場所だけど、行けと言われたしな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:969
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_54741a97:

    # "Fortunately, I manage to find shelter from the storm in the lee of the classroom door."
    "幸い、教室のドアの陰に隠れて、どっと出て行く人ごみをかわすことができた。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:976
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_cf232d59:

    # "Eventually the torrent subsides and I step tentatively out into the hallway."
    "そのうち喧騒も落ち着き、俺はためらいつつ廊下へと踏み出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:978
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_826107a5:

    # "Only to be met by Emi, who comes flouncing down the hallway like a cannonball."
    "すると、笑美がいる。弾丸のように廊下を突っ切ってこっちに来る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:985
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_178c1a74:

    # emi "Hey! Hi Hisao! Great timing!"
    emi "あっ！　ハーイ、久夫くん！　丁度よかったぁ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:990
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c90ae528:

    # emi "I have super extra lunch today, as promised! Let's go upstairs!"
    emi "スーパースペシャルランチ、ちゃんと持ってきたよ、約束通り！　屋上行こうよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:997
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_625a31b5:

    # emi "Hisao!"
    emi "久夫く――ん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1002
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_87d7a3b2:

    # emi "I'm going to make you a one-time-only, super extra special lunch offer!"
    emi "あたし、今回限りの超スーパースペシャルランチを久夫くんにごちそうしちゃいます！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1007
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_388f0dbc:

    # emi "Emi's home made lunch boxes, and the privilege of enjoying them in private with two bombshell beauties!"
    emi "笑美ちゃんお手製のお弁当に、超セクシーな美少女二人が一緒にいてくれるオマケつきなの！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1009
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_32b88a3e:

    # "Her overly flirtatious sales pitch echoes in the hallway, a remarkable feat since it's full of people."
    "笑美の大げさで軽薄な売り込みが廊下に響き渡り、多くの生徒の注目の的になる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1014
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_19e0b6e2:

    # "Emi strikes a very confident-looking pose as though as an attempt to one-up her own ridiculousness, puffing her very modest chest and making the V for victory sign with her hand."
    "おかしな誘いをさらにプッシュするように、笑美は自信満々にポーズを取り、とっても控えめな胸を張ってＶサインをきめる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1016
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4bb9eb12:

    # hi "Sounds delicious. To what do I owe this honor of being invited?"
    hi "そりゃおいしそうだ。俺がご招待にあずかる理由は何かあるのかな？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1021
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_927ff6a6:

    # emi "You stood there looking really lost and sad so I thought you could use some company."
    emi "久夫くん、マジで途方に暮れてて悲しそうに突っ立ってたから、それで一緒にどうかなって思って"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1023
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5ecd4f3b:

    # "That is probably the most depressing reason imaginable."
    "そいつは考えうる限り、もっとも憂鬱な理由だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1028
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_bb90412e:

    # emi "So how about it? You're probably really lonely and would eat that awful cafeteria food all alone, otherwise."
    emi "どうするの？　来ないなら久夫くん、きっと寂しく一人ぼっちで食堂のヒドいご飯を食べることになっちゃうよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1030
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_121fcf67:

    # hi "Eeeh…"
    hi "ええっ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1035
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c247ec5d:

    # emi "I'm kidding, I'm kidding!"
    emi "冗談、冗談だよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1037
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6b348f46:

    # hi "Sure, I'll have your lunch offer. With pleasure."
    hi "わかった、じゃあその話乗るよ。喜んで"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1042
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f1e7fd26:

    # emi "Let's go to the roof!"
    emi "んじゃ、屋上行こ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1044
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fde3210e:

    # hi "The roof?"
    hi "屋上？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1046
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_2a995993:

    # hi "Why the roof?"
    hi "なんで屋上なんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1051
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fa506d3f:

    # emi "Because that's where we eat lunch!"
    emi "そこでお昼食べるからに決まってるじゃん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1053
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_eb9e0386:

    # emi "And if I don't get up there, then she'll probably wander off and then I just know she'll go hungry because she never packs a lunch for herself!"
    emi "それに行かないと、あの子どっかにふらふら行っちゃうし。あの子絶対お弁当持ってこないから、お腹空かせちゃうってわかってるし！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1055
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_915e16a1:

    # hi "Who will?"
    hi "あの子？　誰だよ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1060
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f5afbe6f:

    # emi "Come with me!"
    emi "ほら、行くよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1062
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_36035a32:

    # "Without answering my question or waiting for a response, she grabs me by the arm and drags me through the hallways."
    "質問に答えず、俺の返事も待たずに、笑美は俺の腕を取って廊下を引っ張って行く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1064
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6fd1d024:

    # "I attempt to make conversation on the way."
    "途中、何とか話をしようと試みる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1066
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fe090933:

    # hi "Why do you have an extra lunch?"
    hi "どうして余分に弁当なんて持ってるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1071
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_3fdaa024:

    # "Emi smiles guiltily."
    "笑美は気まずそうに微笑む。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1073
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f3b272fb:

    # emi "Actually, it's yesterday's lunch."
    emi "ホントはね、これ昨日のお弁当なの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1075
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_beca5618:

    # emi "I slipped in a run at lunch and forgot to eat it."
    emi "お昼休みに走ってて、食べるの忘れちゃったの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1077
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a439b59a:

    # "Huh."
    "ふーん。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1080
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_2aa37d6f:

    # "Her expression is so funny that I almost laugh out loud."
    "笑美の表情が可笑しくて、声を出して笑うところだった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1082
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0836c26a:

    # "Emi giggles, to herself or to something or other, or maybe for no reason at all. I like the sound of it."
    "笑美はクスクス笑う。思い出し笑いだったり、誰かのことを笑ったり、何の理由もなかったり、そんな笑い声が俺は好きになる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1084
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_1df98d68:

    # "Emi's sunny, energetic disposition alleviates the constricting feeling in the back of my head from the fight with Shizune and Misha."
    "笑美の陽気で生き生きした性格のおかげで、静音やミーシャとけんかした時から続く、頭を締め付けるような感覚が楽になる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1086
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6b710558:

    # "I let that issue slide out of my mind, and smile for the first time today."
    "俺はそのことを心から追い出し、今日初めて笑う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1094
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9789745f:

    # "The stairway to the roof is a little dilapidated, but it's clearly been used recently."
    "屋上への階段は少しおんぼろだけど、明らかに最近使われた跡がある。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1096
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a1203748:

    # "At the top of the stairs is a door, complete with missing padlock."
    "階段の最上段にあるドアは、南京錠がなくなっている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1098
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5ee68f79:

    # "I wonder who the intrepid individual was that removed the lock?"
    "鍵を取り外した怖いもの知らずなやつは誰なんだろう？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1108
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_094ec31a:

    # "Emi shoves the door open and steps beaming into the sunlight."
    "笑美はドアを強く押し開け、太陽の光が降り注ぐ中へ笑顔で足を踏み入れる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1124
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ee34b0c7:

    # "Suddenly, a tall dark stranger appears out of nowhere, standing imposingly in front of us. Emi flinches back, almost falling back down the stairs."
    "突然、背の高い人影が俺たちの前に姿を現し、堂々と立ちふさがる。たじろいだ笑美は、階段から転げ落ちそうになる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1135
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9e726adf:

    # emi "Yipes! You scared me, Rin!"
    emi "わぁ！　ビックリしたじゃない、琳！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1137
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_46e6d838:

    # "Wait, isn't she…"
    "ちょっと待てよ、こいつは……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1144
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "やあ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1146
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_501f9239:

    # "Noticing that Rin is speaking to me, Emi looks curiously at me."
    "琳が俺に話しかけていると気づき、不思議そうに笑美がこちらを見つめる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1151
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_467e8b70:

    # emi "You two know each other?"
    emi "二人とも知り合い？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1153
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a7b44713:

    # "I look confusedly at Emi."
    "俺はわけが判らなくなって笑美を見る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1155
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_d6f85e0d:

    # hi "She's that friend of yours?"
    hi "こいつがさっき言ってた友達？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1160
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c747a87e:

    # "Rin has turned her gaze towards the clouds drifting above the school."
    "琳は学校の真上を流れる雲へ目を向ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1162
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_50d49c4d:

    # rin "I didn't know you knew this person, Emi."
    rin "笑美、この人と知り合いだったんだ。知らなかったよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1166
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1168
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_010306d6:

    # "The awkward silence lasts only for a few seconds until Emi lets out a tiny giggle, shrugging the coincidence off."
    "気まずい沈黙が流れる。でも笑美がこの偶然に肩をすくめ、小さくクスクス笑いだすと、それもすぐに途絶える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1173
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_2d38c40a:

    # emi "I invited Hisao for lunch. If you know him, that's just better."
    emi "あたしが久夫くんをお昼に誘ったの。琳が久夫くんのこと知ってるなら、ちょうどいいわ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1178
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9c1e5bfe:

    # rin "Oh. Does this mean I don't get food? Or did you invite him for lunch without the lunch?"
    rin "あれ。じゃあ私は昼ご飯なしってこと？　それともお弁当はないけど久夫をお昼に誘ったの？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1183
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a26d7d1c:

    # emi "Erm, neither, I have food for three."
    emi "うーん、どっちもはずれ。三人分用意してるの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1188
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5587e30f:

    # rin "Nice thinking."
    rin "さすがだね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1194
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_73c68c06:

    # "They walk to the other end of the roof while I stay at the clock tower for a while, taking in the atmosphere."
    "笑美たちはお喋りしながら屋上のむこう端へと歩いていく。俺は時計台の辺りで少し立ち止まり、この状況を理解しようとする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1198
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fd9799d0:

    # "There is nobody else but us here. I guess the roof is not as popular as it is in other schools."
    "屋上には俺たち以外誰もいない。ここの屋上は、他の学校ほどには人気のある場所じゃないらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1200
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5928ddbb:

    # "A few rundown benches and tables are scattered around the edges, perhaps in an attempt to make the rooftop look less desolate."
    "屋上の端には、古びたベンチとテーブルが点々と置かれている。ここのわびしい雰囲気を少しでもマシにしようとしたんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1202
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_874d71e8:

    # "The small pebbles covering the roof rattle beneath our feet."
    "俺たちの足元で、屋上を覆う小さな石ころがガラガラと音を立てる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1204
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f37e1693:

    # "I peek through the chain link fence to take a look at the school grounds and beyond."
    "金網フェンスを通して、学校のグラウンドやその彼方が垣間見える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1206
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ab75bf7b:

    # "Students are strolling in pairs and groups around the quadrangle and at the cafeteria."
    "生徒たちは二人組やグループになって、中庭や食堂をぶらついている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1208
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f6ac3200:

    # "A few delivery trucks are driving past the school towards the convenience store nearby."
    "何台か運送トラックが学校の前を通り過ぎ、近所のコンビニのほうへ向かっている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1210
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f7c70f2e:

    # "Somewhere a watchdog barks at a passer-by."
    "どこかで番犬が通行人に向かって吠えている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1212
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_78fc5af6:

    # "Somehow, when I look towards the town center the small town feel strikes me very strongly, almost palpably."
    "街の中心のほうを眺めていると、どうしてなのか、このちっぽけな町の雰囲気に俺の胸が震える。触れたら判りそうなくらいに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1214
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0191dbaa:

    # "The hectic lifestyle of big metropolises seems so far away and foreign here; nobody has to run to catch a bus like their life depended on it or get their senses overloaded by the neon lights and traffic jams."
    "ここだと、大都市での忙しい生活がとても遠く、異質なもののように感じられる。誰もバスに必死で駆け込んだりしないし、ネオンの光や渋滞にくらくらすることもない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1216
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_b732163f:

    # "I feel surprisingly optimistic about this new life of mine, looking at my new hometown, even if it's going to be mine for only one short year."
    "俺の新しい居場所を見渡しながら、ここでの新生活に対してかなり楽観的になる。それがたった一年の間だとしても。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1218
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4bba9a3c:

    # "Finding out about my illness and having to move away from home all came so suddenly I haven't had time to think how I feel about it."
    "病気が見つかったこととか、家を出たりしたことが、何もかも急に起きたおかげで、そのことを自分自身でどう思っているのか、振り返る時間がなかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1220
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0610b39f:

    # "When I step out of the shadow of the clock tower to the open I feel warmth touching my back."
    "時計台の影から広々とした場所に一歩踏み出すと、背中に温もりを感じる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1222
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_1750c6d3:

    # "The sun shines from a perfectly clear cerulean sky."
    "澄み切った青空に太陽が輝いている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1224
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_b2a43009:

    # "A cool breeze sweeping over the rooftop makes me shiver, but only briefly."
    "冷たい風が屋上を通り過ぎ、ほんのわずかだけど体が震える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1226
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5e8a77b3:

    # "The wind carries the scent of trees and flowers, not smog and car exhaust like it used to, just a few weeks ago."
    "風が木や草花の匂いを運んでくる。ほんの数週間前は、風が運んでくるのはスモッグや車の排ガスだけだったのに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1228
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4b2e3997:

    # "Emi settles on a bench with Rin in tow and produces one big and two small lunch boxes from her bag."
    "笑美は琳を従えてベンチに腰掛け、大きな弁当箱１つと小さな弁当箱２つをかばんから取り出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1234
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9b44ff65:

    # emi "Come on, Hisao! What are you waiting for?"
    emi "おいでよ、久夫くん！　早く早く！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1236
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9936cb19:

    # "She is beckoning me to join them, making room on the already small bench."
    "笑美はすでにギュウギュウ詰めのベンチに場所を作り、手招きする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1248
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f95792d3:

    # "I seat myself on the corner of the bench to take as little space as possible. It's pretty cramped, but somehow all three of us fit on it."
    "俺はできるだけ場所を取らないようにベンチの隅に座る。かなり窮屈だけど、なんとか３人収まった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1250
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_208b95e1:

    # hi "Impressive view."
    hi "素敵な眺めだな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1255
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fdf77555:

    # "Emi suppresses a giggle and places a lunchbox in front of Rin, and hands another lunchbox to me."
    "笑美はクスクス笑いをこらえて琳の前に弁当箱を置き、もう一つを俺に手渡す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1260
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9ba54601:

    # emi "Here you go! Lunch, as promised!"
    emi "はいどうぞ！　お約束どおりのお弁当だよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1262
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ab61edd6:

    # "Homemade, no less. I'm impressed."
    "まさしく笑美の手作りだ。すごいもんだな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1264
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_d287f5fc:

    # hi "Wow. This looks really good."
    hi "すげぇ。こりゃマジで美味そうだな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1269
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_e5e041dd:

    # emi "Thanks! I make 'em myself when I can."
    emi "ありがと！　あたし、作れるときは自分でお弁当作るんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1271
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fe85012c:

    # "Conversation dies off as I set about the business of feeding myself."
    "俺が弁当を食べるのに忙しくなると、会話が途切れる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1276
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_77b30cac:

    # "Taking a few bites, I glance up and notice Rin deftly opening the lunch box and popping a forkful of food into her mouth using only her feet."
    "弁当を何口か食べ、チラッと顔を上げると、琳が足だけで器用に弁当箱を開け、フォークでご飯をすくってポイッと口に入れるのに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1278
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0b9bb905:

    # "Even though I've seen it before, I can't help but be impressed at her dexterity."
    "以前にも見たけれど、琳の器用さに感心せずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1280
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_63c407ac:

    # "It's also a reminder of the sort of place I am in right now."
    "そして、自分が今いる場所のことも思い出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1282
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_e515ecff:

    # "Will I ever get used to sights such as this?"
    "こんな光景に慣れることができるのだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1284
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0adaf735:

    # "I can't decide if getting used to such a thing would be a good thing or a bad thing either."
    "慣れることがいいことなのか悪いことなのかも、俺には判断できない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1286
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a7c58160:

    # "Does getting used to this place mean that I'm giving up on being a normal person?"
    "この場所に慣れるってことは、俺が『普通の人間』であることをあきらめるってことなのか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1288
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_97d04087:

    # "Or does it just mean that I'm becoming more understanding about those around me?"
    "それとも、周りにいる人たちのことをもっと思いやれるようになっているだけなのか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1290
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ca9ca7fe:

    # "I'm distracted from my thoughts by the sight of Emi tearing into her lunch as if it had insulted her ancestors."
    "笑美が先祖の仇と戦うかのように弁当をがつがつ食べるのを見て、俺の気が逸れる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1295
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ce0f5e39:

    # hi "You seem pretty hungry."
    hi "なんかかなり腹ペコみたいだけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1300
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0ffacdcd:

    # "Emi looks up, mouth half full, and swallows before nodding."
    "笑美は顔を上げ、口に入ったままの食べ物を飲み込んでうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1302
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_eb239033:

    # emi "My morning run always works up an appetite."
    emi "朝練でいっつも食欲が増すの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1307
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8cbb242c:

    # emi "Which is great, because then I burn through lunch pretty quickly."
    emi "それっていいことなのよ。だってお昼ご飯もすぐに燃えちゃうから"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1312
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_96de0f46:

    # emi "Helps me keep my girlish figure."
    emi "そのおかげで女の子らしいスタイルを保ててるの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1317
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_998c8d6e:

    # rin "What would happen if you'd lose it? Would you become a man?"
    rin "女の子っぽいスタイルがなくなるとどうなるの？　男になっちゃうとか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1319
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4d525ac3:

    # "I very nearly choke on my lunch trying not to laugh."
    "笑いをこらえようとして、昼飯が危うくのどに詰まりそうになる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1324
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_578e09f5:

    # emi "It's a figure of speech."
    emi "言葉のあやよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1329
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_b09d55f7:

    # rin "Does your figure have to run in the mornings too?"
    rin "スタイルも朝走らないといけないの？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1331
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_59481d26:

    # hi "Do you always talk like this?"
    hi "お前ら、いっつもそんな風に話してんのか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1339
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8447ce8b:

    # "I think that answers my question."
    "ああ、今のでよくわかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1341
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_3ce9043d:

    # hi "Er, never mind."
    hi "あぁ、気にすんなって"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1343
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9537656f:

    # hi "So, uh…"
    hi "そうだな、うーん……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1345
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_e8c07606:

    # "I struggle to think of small talk and settle on the obvious question."
    "何か世間話をしようと考えてみるけど、今さらの質問に落ち着く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1347
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4acdef2a:

    # hi "How'd you two meet?"
    hi "二人はどうやって知り合ったんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1352
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f3656475:

    # "Rin seems content to let Emi answer this question."
    "琳は、質問を笑美に答えさせようとしているらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1357
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_dfc747b8:

    # emi "Someone in the housing department thought that we'd complement each other well, so we were assigned rooms next to one another."
    emi "部屋を決める人が、あたしたち互いを補えるだろうって思ったの。だから隣同士の部屋になったってわけ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1359
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4947530b:

    # hi "Complement each other?"
    hi "互いを補う？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1364
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8156c22b:

    # rin "Like shoes and a suit."
    rin "靴と服の関係みたいなもんかな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1366
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "はぁ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1371
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fcc47f4a:

    # "Emi giggles at my confusion."
    "笑美は俺が混乱してるのを見てクスクス笑う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1373
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_eeba2bce:

    # emi "Put us together and we've got all our limbs, get it?"
    emi "一緒にすると、手足が揃うの。わかった？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1375
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9a287fc4:

    # hi "Ah."
    hi "あぁ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1380
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_891b9501:

    # emi "So I started helping Rin get ready in the mornings, and that was that!"
    emi "それであたし、琳の朝の支度を手伝うことにしたの。そういうこと！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1385
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5737bd49:

    # emi "I mean, you can't help someone get dressed every morning and not get along."
    emi "だってさ、毎朝着替えを手伝ってて、仲良くならないわけないでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1387
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "確かにな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1389
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4cf7956c:

    # "Rin chooses this moment to interject."
    "このタイミングを見計らって琳が言葉を差し挟む。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1394
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6b582633:

    # rin "I have trouble with shirts."
    rin "私、シャツ着るの大変なの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1396
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0a385598:

    # hi "Right, that seems… fairly obvious."
    hi "そうだな、そりゃ……見ればわかるよ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1401
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9b9c5dab:

    # rin "Really?"
    rin "ホントに？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1403
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_e9b5b179:

    # hi "Kind of…?"
    hi "なんとなくだけど……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1405
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c680b16e:

    # "This isn't helping, but at least Emi seems to find the whole thing funny."
    "フォローになってない。とはいえ、笑美はこのやり取りを面白がっているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1407
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6d21fb81:

    # "That, combined with the fact that Rin is genuinely curious, makes me feel slightly better and yet, confused."
    "琳が純粋に好奇心から聞いているってこともあり、気持ちは軽くなるものの、まだ俺は困惑している。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1409
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5a115128:

    # hi "I mean, you've got no arms."
    hi "だってほら、ないじゃないか、腕"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1411
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8e20f398:

    # hi "So uh, putting on a shirt seems like one of those things that would be… difficult."
    hi "そんで、えーと、シャツを着たりするのが……難しそうだなって"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1413
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_897ff6e7:

    # "You know what? I'm going to just stop talking now."
    "よし。俺もう話すのやめる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1415
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_83e0e996:

    # "It'll save me a lot of trouble in the long run."
    "長い目で見れば、そのほうがずっと厄介ごとが少なくて済むだろうさ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1417
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_3838a6cb:

    # "Rin nods in what I suspect is meant to be a sage manner."
    "琳は頷く。たぶん思慮深そうな態度のつもりなんだろうけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1422
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_da73fb4c:

    # rin "I see."
    rin "なるほど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1427
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a5569120:

    # "The conversation dies as I turn my attention back to my lunch."
    "俺が弁当に意識を戻すと、また会話がとぎれる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1429
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0868b2c9:

    # "It's really quite good."
    "本当に美味しかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1431
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_97b61309:

    # "Emi finishes her lunch first and makes a contented noise."
    "笑美が最初に弁当を食べ終え、満腹の声を上げる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1436
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_73c6dc4e:

    # emi "Ah, that was good."
    emi "あー、おいしかった"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1438
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a7e4ebd3:

    # "As she busies herself with cleaning up her lunch, Rin speaks up."
    "笑美が忙しく弁当の片付けをしてると、琳が声を上げる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1443
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_71e52ecd:

    # rin "I'm thirsty."
    rin "のど渇いた"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1448
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c14ea7ab:

    # emi "Oh! I almost forgot about that! Sorry!"
    emi "あーっ！　すっかり忘れてた！　ゴメンね！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1453
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9f1e25be:

    # "With a flourish, she reaches into her bag and removes a trio of juiceboxes."
    "見せびらかすように、笑美はかばんからジュースのパックを３本取り出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1455
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_60f68cfc:

    # "She tosses me one that appears to be cranberry juice, one to Rin that appears to be some kind of strawberry milk (complete with pink color scheme), and keeps an (equally pink) box of some kind of fruit punch for herself."
    "俺にクランベリージュースの入ったパックを放り、琳には苺ミルクのようなピンク色のやつを渡し、自分は同じピンクのフルーツパンチらしいパックを取る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1460
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c3df4cb5:

    # "Rin dexterously stabs her straw through the top of her box and begins to drink."
    "琳は器用にストローをパックの上に突き刺して飲み始める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1462
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_434053a7:

    # "I'm once again impressed by how flexible she is, but this time I keep my comment to myself."
    "琳の適応力にまたもや感心してしまうけれど、今回は心の中にしまっておこう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1464
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_d4e86b97:

    # "Somehow I don't think either Emi or Rin are the sorts of people to think twice about the way they work around their particular disabilities."
    "どういうわけか、笑美や琳が、それぞれの障害とどう付き合っていくかをじっくり考えたりするタイプだとは思えない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1466
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6930ae5e:

    # "Rin especially so."
    "特に琳はそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1468
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c6863136:

    # "Indeed, she gives off the impression of being entirely unaware that she's missing any limbs at all."
    "実際、琳からは腕が無いことにまるで気づいてない、そんな印象を受ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1470
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0f358569:

    # "Whether or not that's a conscious decision is another matter."
    "意識してそうしているかいないかはまた別問題だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1472
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8dc876f5:

    # "I'm honestly not sure."
    "正直なところわからない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1477
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_01cfa50e:

    # emi "So Hisao, how do you like it up here?"
    emi "久夫くん、ここの屋上どうだった？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1482
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "んん？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1484
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_2f4c21c4:

    # hi "It's quite nice, actually. I like high places, for the view."
    hi "マジで良かったよ。俺、高い所からの眺めって好きでさ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1486
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_2f23105a:

    # hi "Thanks for inviting me up here."
    hi "屋上に誘ってくれてありがとな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1488
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_911cf72e:

    # hi "And for the lunch, too."
    hi "あと昼飯もな。美味しかったよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1493
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_3c6c8658:

    # "Emi grins a thousand-watt grin, pleased by my response I suppose."
    "笑美は１０００ワットの笑顔でニッコリと微笑む。俺の反応に喜んだから、だと思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1495
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_0663d380:

    # emi "No problem!"
    emi "どういたしまして！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1500
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8118bcf6:

    # emi "Feel free to eat with us next time too, okay?"
    emi "またいつでも一緒に食べに来てよ、ね？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1502
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_302b587f:

    # emi "I won't make you a lunch, but you can bring your own up here."
    emi "久夫くんのお弁当は作らないけど、自分のを持ってくればいいから"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1504
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_7ad08b1f:

    # hi "No lunch service? I don't know…"
    hi "お弁当はナシかよ？　どうしようかな……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1509
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_970a22ee:

    # "Emi looks mock offended."
    "笑美は拗ねたふりをする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1511
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_3e15217c:

    # emi "Trying to take advantage of my good nature?"
    emi "あたしの親切に乗っかろうとしてるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1513
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_d9c07710:

    # emi "The nerve!"
    emi "ずうずうしいんだから！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1518
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_8f6c5e0e:

    # "She giggles."
    "笑美がクスクス笑う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1523
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f26eaeb9:

    # emi "Well, if that's your answer, I guess Rin and I will just keep eating lunch all alone…"
    emi "そうね、それが久夫くんの答えなら、あたし、ずっと琳と二人だけでお昼食べるから……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1525
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_b67a056d:

    # "I am suddenly assaulted by the most heart-rending puppy-dog eyes I've ever seen as Emi pouts."
    "ふくれっ面をした笑美の、今までで一番にキュートな子犬みたいな瞳が俺に不意打ちを食らわす。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1527
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_40493883:

    # hi "Kidding! I was kidding!"
    hi "冗談！　冗談だってば！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1529
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_d9faf670:

    # hi "I'd love to eat lunch up here again."
    hi "もちろんまたここで昼飯を食べるよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1531
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_6cc626c5:

    # hi "Good location, and the company's okay too."
    hi "眺めもいいし、メンバーも悪くないしな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1536
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9386ac6d:

    # "Emi frowns a bit at my declaration of 'okay' but seems happy enough that I've accepted her invitation."
    "笑美は『悪くない』って言い方にちょっとまゆを寄せたけど、俺が誘いを受けてくれたことはとても嬉しいみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1538
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_cc8dad80:

    # "I guess this makes us friends now."
    "これで、俺たちは友達なのかな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1540
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9cde03ce:

    # "Or at least acquaintances."
    "少なくとも知り合いかな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1544
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_2c14f975:

    # "The lunch bell rings, signaling a return downstairs."
    "昼休みの終わりのベルが鳴る。階下に戻る時間だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1549
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ff595721:

    # emi "Rin, you didn't finish your lunch again!"
    emi "ちょっと琳、またご飯残してる！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1554
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_7ca8c604:

    # rin "I wasn't that hungry."
    rin "私、そこまでお腹すいてなかったんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1559
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_90c1aa11:

    # emi "If you don't eat more, you're going to fade away!"
    emi "もう、ちゃんと食べなきゃ、そのうち消えてなくなっちゃうよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1564
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_bad8c8b9:

    # "Rin shrugs, as if this is an acceptable risk."
    "琳は肩をすくめる。それでも構わないと言わんばかりに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1568
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a0d5f79a:

    # hi "Come on, we'd better get going."
    hi "ほら、もう行かないとだぜ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1575
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_ea28ad6d:

    # "The three of us head down the stairs together."
    "三人揃って階段を下りる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1580
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_a9a65e73:

    # "The afternoon class passes. Once again, I find myself without a plan for something to do after school, so I head to the library to return a couple of the books I finished reading."
    "午後の授業は過ぎていく。またしても放課後の予定がないことに気づき、読み終えた本を何冊か返しに図書室へ向かうことにする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1588
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_4fc98d86:

    # "Walking inside, I see that there are about as many students here as there were on Tuesday, all the more evident from the almost total silence enveloping the room."
    "図書室の中を歩くと、火曜日と同じぐらいしか生徒がいないことがわかる。部屋全体を包む、せき一つない静寂からもそのことは明らかだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1601
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_74b27c99:

    # "As I drop the books I'd borrowed into the returns slot in the counter, Yuuko suddenly pops up from behind it, quite startled from the banging they make as they hit the trolley next to her."
    "借りた本をカウンターの返却口に放り込むと、優子さんが突然その後ろから飛び出す。本が彼女の隣にあるトレイに当たって立てたバンという音で驚いたらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1603
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_7310bf6c:

    # hi "Ah, sorry Yuuko. Didn't mean to startle you."
    hi "あ、すみません、優子さん。驚かすつもりじゃなかったんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1608
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_772e4bae:

    # yu "No, no. That's fine. It happens… a lot. I'm used to it by now."
    yu "ううん、いいの。大丈夫だから。こんなことは……しょっちゅうあるの。もう慣れちゃったから"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1613
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_9d83e081:

    # yu "Um, can I help you?"
    yu "あ、何か手伝おうか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1615
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c50be686:

    # hi "It's okay, I think I know where everything is. Thanks anyway."
    hi "大丈夫ですよ。どこに何があるかはわかってますから。ありがとうございます"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1620
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_759d26ee:

    # "I suppose I'll grab another book or two while I'm here. There's not much else to do, and after reading so much during my stay in the hospital, it's become a hard habit to break."
    "１、２冊本を借りていこうか。そんなにすることもないし、病院に入院してる間にたくさん本を読んだせいで、本を読まずにはいられなくなってしまっている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1624
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_183ab4b9:

    # "I wander down to the fiction section towards the back of the library, scanning the bookshelves for anything that catches my eye."
    "何か目ぼしい本がないか探しながら小説の区画辺りをぶらつき、図書室の奥へと向かう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1626
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_61d4bfb7:

    # "As I do, I look over to the corner where Hanako had been the last time I was here, not really expecting anything to come of it."
    "そうしながらも、以前華子に出会った本棚の角のあたりを見渡す。何かを期待していたわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1631
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_66a61c9e:

    # "…surprisingly, though, she's there, absorbed completely in a fairly thick book. I decide against intruding on her like last time and get back to finding reading material."
    "……けど、意外にも華子がいて、すっかり分厚い本に夢中になっている。邪魔するのはやめようと思い、本を探しに戻る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1638
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_7fa7d3b5:

    # "After an indiscernible amount of time spent perusing the aisles, I finally decide on a couple of books to get and slide them off the shelf."
    "それからどれくらい経っただろうか、通路の本棚全部に目を通し、ようやく俺は２冊の本を取り出す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1640
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_5a006c53:

    # "With a minimum of fuss, I quickly walk over to the counter, check out my books and pop them into my bag as I walk out."
    "寄り道せずに素早くカウンターへ向かって本を借り、かばんへ入れつつ図書室を出る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1645
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_d6c539d1:

    # "By the time I leave the main building, sunset isn't too far away. A small trickle of students remain, but the majority have left; presumably to their homes and dorms."
    "本校舎を離れるころには、日暮れが近くなっていた。残ってる生徒たちがポツポツと出てくるけど、大半の生徒はとっくに校舎からいなくなっている。たぶん自宅か寮に戻ってるんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1651
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c6c00024:

    # "Feeling utterly drained, I head to my room to read the books I borrowed. There's been enough action and excitement for one day already."
    "俺はすっかり疲れた気分になって、借りた本を読もうと自室へ戻る。もう十分過ぎるくらいの運動と興奮のあった一日だし。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1653
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_f87ec8ad:

    # "The first is 'Alice's Adventures in Wonderland'. I know the story, of course, but I've never actually read the original book."
    "まずは『不思議の国のアリス』だな。もちろんこの話は知ってるけど、原本を読んだことは一度もない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1655
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_fb6748d4:

    # "It's just as trippy as I remember the story to be, with the wacky characters and nonsense plot."
    "いかれた登場人物やナンセンスな筋書き、覚えていた通り、奇抜な物語だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1657
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_c8637897:

    # "I start thinking of myself as some kind of an Alice too, haplessly tumbling down the rabbit hole into this Cripple Wonderland."
    "俺は自分のことをアリスのように考え始める。不運にもウサギの穴から転がり落ちて、たどり着いたのは『かたわの国』。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1659
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_16ea35e9:

    # "…Okay, that's a rather strong expression. Still, the isolated location and the overt way the school accommodates to absolutely everything is unsettling. It is like another world."
    "……いや、今のはひどい言い方だ。それでもこの孤立した立地と、なにもかもをありのまま受け入れるこの学校のやり方は落ち着かない。ここは全くの別世界みたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1661
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_31bb9666:

    # "I wonder why I can't shake the feeling of being an outsider like Alice, despite most everyone being so hospitable and friendly with me."
    "どうして、自分がアリスみたいによそ者だという感覚を振り落とすことができないんだろう。ここの人々のほとんどはとても親切で友好的なのに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1663
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_42c091b6:

    # "Turning another page, my mind starts drifting further away from the book. It's quiet, I can hear my heartbeat thumping against the fabric of my shirt."
    "ページをめくりながら、俺の意識はさらに本から離れていく。心臓の鼓動がシャツの布地に打ち付ける音が聞こえそうなくらい静かだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1665
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_7c506c7d:

    # "For some reason, it makes me feel really bad like it has since that time in the forest with Iwanako. Like I was locked in a cage with something nasty and scary."
    "どういうわけか、岩魚子に森で会ったあの時のように、マジで心地が悪くなる。気持ち悪くて恐ろしい何かと、一緒の檻に閉じ込められたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1672
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_62286fc3:

    # "I put the book down for a while and stare at the ceiling, taking my time to shake off the feeling."
    "しばらく本を置き、天井を見つめ、ゆっくりと嫌な気持ちを振り払う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1674
translate jp a1_friday_foot_and_mouth_86cca162:

    # "200 pages later, I fall asleep."
    "２００ページを過ぎたあたりで、俺は眠りに落ちる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1688
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_14d63eff:

    # "I guess I need to buy some supplies. I can't live off cafeteria food and eating out for my entire stay here."
    "何か食べ物を買ってこないとな。ここにいる間、ずっと学食や外食だけで食いつなぐわけにはいかない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1693
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e6213912:

    # "As I leave for the gate, I make a few loud stretches to try and stave off the tiredness that's accumulated over the week."
    "門に向かいながら、この一週間の疲れを払いのけるように何度か大きく伸びをする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1700
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a3cb0780:

    # "After passing through and rounding the corner, though, I see a solitary figure walking downhill towards the small town below. The color of her hair and tapping of her cane are unmistakable."
    "門を抜けて角を曲がると、小さな町へと続く下り坂を一人きりで歩く人影が見える。あの髪の色と、杖を突く音は間違えようがない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1706
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_33e2a0f5:

    # "I quickly walk up to her, which seems to catch her attention without a word needing to be said."
    "早足で追いつく。声をかけるまでもなく、こちらに気づいたようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1708
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4d5294c9:

    # hi "Hi, Lilly."
    hi "よう、リリー"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1713
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_2452fa11:

    # "She takes a moment to place the voice, slightly adjusting her head to face a bit more towards the source of my voice as she does."
    "リリーは口を開くまでに少し間を置き、俺の声がしたほうへとわずかに顔を向ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1718
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_3f263087:

    # li "…Hisao?"
    li "……久夫さん？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1720
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1f8702af:

    # hi "Yep, that's me."
    hi "うん、俺だよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1722
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e8c48abb:

    # "She seems to have a good memory for voices. The fact that she actually remembered is a pleasant surprise."
    "リリーは声を聞き分けるのが得意みたいだ。ちゃんと覚えてくれていたことに驚いた。なんだか嬉しくなる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1724
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_361aad57:

    # li "Good evening. What brings you here?"
    li "こんばんは。どうしてこちらに？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1729
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_c51a5a94:

    # "Once again, she gives a small polite bow. And, once again, I reply in kind before realizing that I needn't do so."
    "またも礼儀正しくおじぎをしてくれる。必要ないんだと気づく前に、俺もまた礼で応じてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1731
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_810e504a:

    # hi "Just going into town. You?"
    hi "町に行こうとしてたんだ。君は？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1736
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4c9cc35b:

    # li "My my, what a coincidence."
    li "あらあら、なんて偶然なんでしょう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1738
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_547697f3:

    # hi "Doing the same thing, eh?"
    hi "同じことしようとしてた？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1743
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_18e73d34:

    # li "Mm. I usually go shopping on Fridays."
    li "ええ。いつも金曜日はお買い物に出かけるんですよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1748
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_cb0fbc9a:

    # "She pauses for a moment, suddenly looking a little lost."
    "リリーはふと立ち止まる。まるで、少し道に迷ったかのように。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1750
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1b02e0a1:

    # li "That said, Hanako usually comes into town with me…"
    li "ですけど、いつもは華ちゃんが一緒に町に行ってくれるんです……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1752
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d6a80fb6:

    # "Ah. Not lost, but worried. The two do seem to keep pretty close tabs on one another. It's kind of surprising that Hanako would just forget Lilly like that."
    "ああ、華子を心配してたのか。確かに、二人はお互いをかなり気にかけてるみたいだし。こんなふうに華子がリリーのことを忘れるなんて、ちょっと意外だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1754
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_634b508a:

    # hi "I noticed her reading in the library. She probably just got caught up in a book."
    hi "そうだ、華子は図書室で本を読んでたよ。きっと夢中になってるだけじゃないかな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1759
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4214b356:

    # "She lets out a small sigh of relief."
    "リリーは胸を撫で下ろす。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1761
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_cb3cc7d5:

    # li "Thank you. She has a habit of doing that."
    li "そうでしたか。あの子はよくそういうことをするんですよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1763
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_67cf06e1:

    # hi "Avid reader?"
    hi "本の虫ってこと？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1768
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_de8f5423:

    # li "Right. She doesn't like being around crowds of people, so reading away from everyone lets her relax a bit."
    li "そうなんですよ。華ちゃんは人ごみが苦手で。みんなから離れて読書しているほうが安心するんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1770
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e0208fbb:

    # "Although she probably didn't intend it, I can't help but grimace as I recall my first meeting with her."
    "リリーにそんなつもりはなかったんだろうけど、俺は華子と初めて出会った時のことを思い出し、苦い顔をしてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1775
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7a9cc922:

    # "Hardly wanting to bring it up, I remain silent as we quietly continue to walk down the quiet road."
    "そのことにはあまり触れたくなくて、俺はそのまま黙りこむ。静かな道を、二人はただ静かに歩き続ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1777
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e847c9ea:

    # "Tack, tack. Tack, tack."
    "コツ、コツ。コツ、コツ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1779
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ac59242d:

    # "With the road bereft of cars and the students of Yamaku increasingly far behind us, the quiet rustling of the leaves and the measured tapping of Lilly's cane against the sidewalk are all that can be heard."
    "道路に車はいないし、山久の生徒たちは遥か後ろだ。聞こえるのは木々のかすかなざわめきと、リリーが白杖で地面を叩くリズミカルな音だけ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1781
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_045b2fc7:

    # "It's kind of nice, especially compared to the hustle and bustle of where I used to live."
    "なんだかいいな。俺が住んでた所の喧噪と比べると、特に。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1783
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_01fcb8a7:

    # "Before I know it, I've relaxed so much that a loud yawn escapes before I can control it."
    "気が抜けていたのか、思わず大きなあくびがでてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1788
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_df893cae:

    # li "Tired?"
    li "疲れましたか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1790
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_634a5586:

    # hi "Yeah, been running ragged these past few days."
    hi "まあね、ここ数日はボロボロになってたから"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1792
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_16b2d15b:

    # "That's an understatement, to be sure. Transferring into a different school would be bad enough, but nothing like this…"
    "正直、これでも控えめな言い方だ。普通は転校するだけでも大変なのに、これだもんな……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1797
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_12e79126:

    # li "Well, hopefully everything should settle down for you. The festival's got everyone in a spin right now, and you've been plopped right in the middle of things."
    li "まあ。何もかもうまく落ち着くといいですね。学園祭で皆さんが大わらわな中に、あなたは放り込まれてしまったわけですから"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1799
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_571cc6c7:

    # "For a moment I hesitate, but given her apparent tolerance for frankness I decide to give my full thoughts."
    "少しの間、俺はためらう。でもリリーなら、本音を言ってもうまく受け止めてくれるだろう。洗いざらい話してみることにする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1801
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_39c86a71:

    # hi "I guess. Yamaku's kind of different though. I mean, the formality surrounding everything, the isolation around it… not to mention the most obvious difference."
    hi "そうかもね。でも山久って、何かが違うんだ。ほら、なにもかも堅苦しいところとか、人里離れた環境とか……一番の違いは言うまでもないけどね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1803
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4d1bd58b:

    # hi "It's kind of a whole different mindset. I suppose I'll get used to it though, in time."
    hi "なんていうか、物の見方がまるっきり違うみたいなんだ。そのうち俺も慣れると思うけどね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1808
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a3bf025e:

    # "She gives a matter-of-fact nod, apparently pleased with my answer. It feels almost as if she's included me in the flock of students she's shepherding, along with class 3-2 and Hanako."
    "リリーはその通りだと言いたげにうなずく。どうやら俺の答えがお気に召したらしい。なんだか、リリーの率いる３－２の生徒たちと華子の仲間にされたような気分だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1810
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_07093d8a:

    # "Well, not that I mind. It's nice to get the thoughts off my chest in any case."
    "まあ、悪い気はしない。なんにしたって胸の内を打ち明けられて良かった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1815
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_180436ec:

    # li "Looking on the bright side, one could see it as a chance for a new beginning. You should cherish the ability to make new friends."
    li "前向きに見れば、新しいスタートのチャンスじゃありませんか。新しい友達を作る、というのは素晴らしいことですよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1817
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_395f844c:

    # "That's optimistic. Nonetheless, it's good to have a positive attitude about such things, I suppose."
    "楽天的な考え方だな。とはいえ、前向きな態度でいるのは良いことなんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1819
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_91b00e83:

    # hi "I guess that's a good take on it."
    hi "そう思ったほうがいいんだろうね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1827
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_5bceb407:

    # "Walking on down the road, she seems to become somewhat unsettled. Before I can ask what's on her mind, she seems to collect herself and speaks up about something else."
    "道を歩いているうちに、リリーがなんだかそわそわし始める。どうしたのか聞く前に、彼女は気を取り直したように別の話を始める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1832
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_3a5524ea:

    # li "So, where in town were you going?"
    li "それで、町のどちらに行くつもりなんですか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1834
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_b8bbbbf5:

    # "That's actually a pretty good question. I'd come in to buy food, but the layout of the place is still totally foreign to me."
    "とてもいい質問だ。食べ物を買いに来たつもりだけど、町のどこに何があるのか、まだ全然わかっていない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1836
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_95f1d360:

    # "I had intended to just wander around and see what I could find, but with sunset already approaching and nightfall not too far away, that doesn't seem very wise."
    "ただ適当にぶらついて何か見つかればと思っていたけど、すでに日は沈みかけていて、夜ももうすぐだし、それはあまり賢明ではなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1838
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_21f8b41a:

    # "I'm going to have to ask her for directions. Again."
    "リリーに道を尋ねるしかなさそうだ。またしても。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1840
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_568c6de2:

    # hi "I was just going to get some food… but now that you mention it, I don't really know the way."
    hi "何か食べ物を買いに行くところだったんだけど……そう言われてみると俺、どこに行けばいいかよくわからないや"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1845
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_dcf94ba8:

    # li "Well now, this is quite lucky. I was just about to go to the convenience store myself."
    li "あら、それはちょうど良かったです。私、コンビニに行くところだったんですよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1847
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_0291098b:

    # hi "Looks like I'll be in your care again, then. Thanks."
    hi "じゃあ、またお世話になるみたいだね。ありがとう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1849
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_29936b81:

    # "Together we walk to the store, my paces carefully slowed to remain beside her. Compared to my usual walking pace, hers is quite a bit slower. Not that it's without reason."
    "目的の店まで一緒に歩く。リリーの横にいられるように、俺は注意深くペースを落とす。俺が普段歩く速さに比べると、リリーはかなり遅い。もちろん、理由はあるんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1856
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7eddb234:

    # "After what couldn't be more than several minutes, I catch sight of our objective. This town really is pretty small."
    "何分かたって、目的地が見えてくる。この町は本当に狭い。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1861
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_c1145ed4:

    # "Without further ado, we make our way inside with a greeting from the counter."
    "あとはこともなく、俺たちは中に入る。レジカウンターからいらっしゃいませと声がかかる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1866
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e97aaf35:

    # li "Mind if I tag along with you? Usually Hanako would help me, but seeing as she's not here…"
    li "あなたについて行っても良いでしょうか？　いつもは華ちゃんが私を手助けしてくれるんですけど、いないので……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1868
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4b581584:

    # "It takes a moment before I realize what she means."
    "その意味がわかるまで少し時間が掛かる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1870
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_f762e479:

    # "Considering she wouldn't be able to read any of the labels, shopping without any help would be a big pain for her."
    "ラベルを読めないということもあるし、リリーにとって助けなしに買い物をするのはかなり辛いことなんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1872
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d866c47c:

    # "That said, I can't shake the feeling that she'd had this idea since I said I was coming here."
    "とはいえ、俺がここに行くと言ったときから、リリーはこうするつもりだったんじゃないか、という気がしてならない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1874
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_c0f73692:

    # hi "Sure. It'd be my pleasure."
    hi "もちろんかまわないよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1876
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_bb7567b7:

    # "I grab two well-used red baskets from the small stack beside the entrance, handing one to Lilly."
    "入り口の横に低く積まれた、使い古された赤いカゴを二つ掴み、一つをリリーに手渡す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1888
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_287ec642:

    # "She lays it on the ground, putting her schoolbag in, retracting her cane and sliding it through the basket's handles before picking it back up in her right hand."
    "リリーはそれを地面に降ろして通学かばんを入れ、白杖を縮めてカゴの取っ手に通し、また右手で持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1890
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d629534e:

    # "Wait, if she doesn't use her cane…"
    "待てよ、リリーが杖を使わないということは……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1895
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_48662f46:

    # "Before I can complete the thought, she comes beside me and pinches the cuff of my uniform in her slender fingers."
    "考えがまとまる前に、リリーは俺のそばに寄り、か細い指で俺の制服の袖をつまむ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1900
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ec4fa69c:

    # li "Is this all right?"
    li "いいですか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1902
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a389cad4:

    # hi "Ah, sure."
    hi "あー、もちろん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1907
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_efe6e3d8:

    # "I have no reason not to accept. I can think of worse things than shopping with a pretty girl holding onto me, even if it is out of necessity."
    "拒む理由はない。やむを得ないとはいえ、かわいい子が俺にすがりついてくるのは悪い話じゃない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1909
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1047cdbb:

    # "We navigate our way through the store, with not one of the occasional passing customers seeming to bat an eyelid."
    "俺たちは店内を進んでいく。時折すれ違う他の客は、顔色一つ変えない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1911
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a006227b:

    # "Considering how close Yamaku is, I guess seeing students from there must be entirely normal for the local residents."
    "山久からの近さを思うと、学園の生徒を目にすること自体は、地元の人からすればまるで普通のことなんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1913
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_83f0950b:

    # "As we reach each aisle, I quickly check with Lilly and find out what she needs. I grab it along with what I'm looking for, and put our items into their respective baskets."
    "各コーナーに行くごとに、手早くリリーに確認して必要なものを聞く。俺が探しているものも一緒に取って、それぞれのカゴに商品を入れる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1915
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d3794cb4:

    # "I guess this is the same routine she and Hanako follow every Friday."
    "これがリリーと華子の、金曜日の日課なのだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1917
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ff16fdd5:

    # hi "Right, all that's left is the bread and that should be my shopping done. Do you need anything else, Lilly?"
    hi "よし、あとはパンだけだ。これで俺の買い物は済んだと思うよ。リリー、他に何かいるものはある？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1922
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_37f84067:

    # li "No, this should be everything."
    li "いいえ、これで全部ですよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1924
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_efb676c2:

    # hi "Off we go, then."
    hi "じゃあ行こうか"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1929
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_99685fd4:

    # "With a quick side trip to the bakery section, we make our way to the registers."
    "パンのコーナーにちょっと立ち寄ってから、俺たちはレジへと向かう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1931
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4f09c8bf:

    # "The line, thankfully, is almost nonexistent. It's not long before we've both paid for our food and are out the door."
    "ありがたいことに、レジで待っている人はほとんどいない。俺たちはすぐに会計を済ませ、店を出る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1938
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_176e7728:

    # "As Lilly retrieves her cane and extends it to full length, I waste a minute looking upwards at the night sky while holding both our bags."
    "リリーは白杖を取り出して、元通りに伸ばす。俺は２人分の買い物袋を持ちながら、少しの間夜空を見上げて時間をつぶす。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1940
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6a98d03d:

    # "For a moment I try to make clouds with my breath, but the summer's heat doesn't seem to cooperate."
    "つかの間、白い息を吐こうとしてみるけど、この夏の熱気では無理がある。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1942
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_3d84df8a:

    # "Eventually she rights herself, taking a quick stretch before taking her bag and leaving me to my two."
    "やがてリリーは立ち上がり、さっと伸びをして自分の袋を手に取る。俺の分は袋二つだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1948
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_8e2bfe59:

    # hi "You tired as well?"
    hi "リリーも疲れてる？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1953
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_70c5b197:

    # li "The festival preparations have been complete chaos. Shizune breathing down my neck doesn't exactly help things, either."
    li "学園祭の準備が本当に忙しかったものですから。羽加道さんにうるさくつきまとわれても、状況はあまり変わらないんですけどね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1955
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_f5964e51:

    # hi "Hey, she's only trying to get everything organized. Better now than later, right?"
    hi "まあ、あいつは物事を進めようとしてただけだよ。善は急げ、だろ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1960
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_29b85bfd:

    # li "I suppose. I'm going to enjoy relaxing in town tomorrow, that's for certain."
    li "そうかもしれません。とにかく明日は町で気晴らしをするつもりです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1962
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d4602b78:

    # "I guess the festival preparations must be taking their toll on both of them."
    "学園祭の準備で、二人とも気が立っているんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1967
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_b4b75df3:

    # "We walk out into the quiet street, talking between ourselves as we carry our bags of food and supplies from the store."
    "コンビニ袋を手に、二人で話をしながら、俺たちはひっそりした通りへと差し掛かる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1969
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_36e2ae8f:

    # "…Wait, what's that?"
    "……待て。あれはなんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1971
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_eb52d744:

    # "I notice a very distinctive figure making its way towards us, silhouetted by the streetlamps."
    "街灯の光に浮かび上がった、とても独特な人影が俺たちに向かってくるのに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1973
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_731dcdd5:

    # "For a second I think it's another male student from my class, but as he, or should I say she, gets closer I recognize her quickly."
    "一瞬、俺のクラスの男子かと思う。けど彼、いや、彼女が近づいてくるにつれ、すぐに誰だか見分けがつく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1984
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4d580195:

    # hi "Rin? What're you doing out here so late?"
    hi "琳か？　こんな遅くにここで何やってんだよ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1989
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_666d46a0:

    # li "Rin?"
    li "りんさん？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1991
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1a4aeb4a:

    # "Lilly perks her head, looking like she's trying to focus on listening more keenly. It suddenly comes to me that I should probably interpret the scene for her."
    "リリーは頭をぴんと上げ、周りの音を聞き逃すまいと集中しているようだ。俺が状況を説明してあげないと、と気づく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1993
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6c84ee20:

    # hi "It's Rin… Tezuka, I think was her last name, from our school."
    hi "琳だよ……名字は手塚だったと思う。ほら、俺たちの学園の"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:1998
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_fe2a08d5:

    # "She stiffens at the name and gives a complicated-looking expression, something like a forced fusion of a composed smile and a painful cringe."
    "リリーはその名前を聞いて硬くなり、複雑な表情を浮かべる。作り笑いと、苦々しいしかめ面を無理矢理混ぜ合わせたような。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2000
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_9932ce09:

    # li "Ah. I understand."
    li "ああ。わかりました"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2002
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_8e3806fd:

    # "I guess Lilly knows Rin too."
    "リリーも琳を知ってるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2012
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_81454cdf:

    # "Rin turns to look at us, looking terribly out of it. I'm not entirely sure if she recognizes either of us or at least she doesn't acknowledge it if she does."
    "琳はとてもぼんやりした様子でこちらを向く。俺たちに気づいていないのか、気づいてはいても、俺たちが誰だかわかっていないのか。どうにも確信が持てない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2014
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_f28c3f4d:

    # "She looks like a zombie. Or a statue. A statue of a zombie."
    "ゾンビみたいだ。銅像かな。いや、ゾンビの銅像か。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2016
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_9d91eec7:

    # "But slowly, some symptoms of understanding seem to light in her dark eyes: this is something she must react to."
    "しかし徐々に、状況を理解したような兆しが暗い瞳にきらめく。私はこれに何か反応しなくてはいけないのだ、と。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2024
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_98780d8f:

    # "Rin blinks once. Very thoroughly."
    "琳は瞬きをひとつする。とてもじっくりと。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2029
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "やあ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2031
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2033
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d9bd4e2f:

    # "There is an awkward pause, everyone waiting for someone else to say something."
    "気まずい沈黙だ。みんな誰かが何か言うのを待っている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2035
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1854d757:

    # hi "What are you doing here this late?"
    hi "こんな遅くに、ここで何してるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2037
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2039
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6d1989e6:

    # rin "I…"
    rin "私……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2044
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e2d2d601:

    # rin "I was wondering about that myself too. Just now."
    rin "自分でも考えてたんだ、そのこと。たった今"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2051
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6db1ed61:

    # rin "Some people asked that just before. I assume they were wondering the same."
    rin "さっきも何人かの人がそう聞いていったよ。みんな同じように不思議がってた"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2053
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d1b304ea:

    # rin "I didn't know. They didn't know either. I asked. That's why I'm wondering."
    rin "私は知らなかった。その人たちも知らなかった。聞いてみたんだ。だから私も不思議に思ってるの"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2055
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ab1fd5c3:

    # rin "So that was pretty much it. It's a murder mystery without a murder."
    rin "大体そんなとこ。殺人事件の推理みたいだね。人は死んでないけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2057
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2062
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ac020c06:

    # rin "They were going that way."
    rin "その人たちならあっちに行ったよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2067
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4ade8cf7:

    # "She turns facing to her right in order to demonstrate the direction the other people went to as if that was important, then rotates back like a mechanical puppet in one of those overly complicated clockworks."
    "まるで大事なことのように、琳は他の人が行った方向を指し示して右を向く。そして、時計仕掛けの凝ったカラクリ人形みたいにこっちに向き直る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2069
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_14855536:

    # "For a person who gives an impression of being the quiet type, Rin really does use a lot of words to say things that don't need a lot to be said."
    "おとなしそうな印象を与えるタイプの割には、琳は手短に済むことについても長々と喋る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2071
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_81d1a346:

    # "Unsure if she's finished, I say nothing. Neither does Lilly, who seems equally robbed of words for the time being."
    "琳が話し終わったのかがわからず、俺は何も言わない。今のところ、リリーも言葉が出ないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2073
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_3d010491:

    # "I think that both of us are in fact just scared that any response might provoke her to continue."
    "本当のところ、うっかり琳を刺激して、また喋り出されることが二人とも怖いんだと思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2075
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7cda2de5:

    # "Our stupefied lack of reaction doesn't faze Rin at all. She keeps looking at us expectantly, a calm hint of expression on her blank face."
    "俺たちは呆然として反応できずにいるけど、琳は全くうろたえない。こっちを期待に満ちた目で見続けている。無表情な顔に浮かぶ感情らしいものはそれだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2077
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1c779c7c:

    # "She seems to be that kind of person. Always so relaxed."
    "琳はそういう人間らしい。いつもそうやってのんきにしていて。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2079
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a314d94d:

    # "As if bull elephant-grade sedatives were flowing in her veins in the place of blood."
    "血のかわりにオス象用の鎮静剤が血管の中に流れているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2084
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6d381216:

    # li "Do you have amnesia? I don't recall you having anything of the sort, though…"
    li "健忘症なんですか？　でも琳さん、そういう症状をお持ちでしたっけ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2086
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_959fc56c:

    # hi "No, I don't think it's that."
    hi "いや、そうじゃないと思うぞ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2088
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_689addc8:

    # hi "The other passersby were probably just worried, though. You do look really lost, the way you're standing in the middle of the street."
    hi "まあ、通りがかった人たちは心配しただけだろう。本気で迷子になったように見えるよ。そうやって道のど真ん中で立ってたりしたら"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2093
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1e6f8d91:

    # rin "Oh, I see."
    rin "ああ、なるほど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2098
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_9c6b9499:

    # rin "Maybe I should've taken some other kind of pose in that case."
    rin "だったら、もっと別のポーズで立ってたほうが良かったかもね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2100
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_40f3a7c0:

    # "I ponder for a while whether I should chase this angle further, or give up for the sake of my own sanity."
    "このことをさらに深追いするべきか、俺の正気を保つために見切りをつけてしまおうか、しばらく頭を悩ませる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2102
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_eb122d1f:

    # "I decide on the latter."
    "俺は後者に決める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2104
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_dfd9c83d:

    # "It seems that most of the time, it's better to not read too deeply into what Rin is babbling about."
    "大抵の場合、琳の無駄口は深読みしない方がいいらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2106
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ef758d06:

    # "Talking with Rin is like playing chess with a supercomputer who does seemingly completely random moves as if to mock everything you know about chess. It's like that, except with human interaction."
    "琳と話していると、チェスの定石を馬鹿にするように滅茶苦茶に駒を動かす、スーパーコンピューターと勝負をしているみたいだ。人間だけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2108
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_b787854c:

    # "And even if I win, it feels like losing."
    "そして、たとえ勝っても負けたような気分になるんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2110
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_160b0f5e:

    # "Damn, it's just like Kenji said. Even when I win, I lose. Is this the power of the girls of Yamaku?"
    "くそ、まさしく健二が言ってた通りじゃないか。俺が勝ったとしても、俺の負け。これが、山久学園の女子のパワーか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2112
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2114
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_2386c2c7:

    # "I push the thought aside as too dangerous to consider further. It's probably just Kenji's anti-female propaganda getting to me during a moment of weakness."
    "この先を考えると危険すぎるので、頭の隅に押しやる。たぶん、まいっているせいで、健二の反女性プロパガンダが心に入り込んできたんだな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2116
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a8484d48:

    # hi "Yeah, maybe taking another pose might have worked."
    hi "そうだな、ポーズを変えれば役には立ったかもな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2118
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_94251d21:

    # hi "So anyway, you have no idea what you're doing here?"
    hi "それはそうと、本当にここで何をしてるかわからないのか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2123
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_1076c3e6:

    # "She frowns, looking extremely displeased at either my question, its consequences, or the answer she's about to give."
    "琳は眉をひそめる。俺の質問、この会話の流れ、自分が言おうとしている答え、そのどれかが非常に気に入らないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2125
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_75a9b4d6:

    # rin "I do have. Some idea. I can't really tell what kind of an idea."
    rin "わかってるよ。少しは。それがなんなのかはうまく説明できないけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2130
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_5d16a00e:

    # li "That sounds like progress, at least."
    li "あら、それなら一歩前進じゃないですか"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2132
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7f3fafed:

    # "Lilly sounds as if she's spotted an opening for some kind of discernibly normal conversation. I can't say I share her optimism."
    "何かまともな会話の糸口を見つけたような話しぶりだ。俺はリリーほど楽観的な気持ちにはなれない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2134
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_31c62969:

    # rin "Yes, there is some. Definitely. The rest will come later."
    rin "そう、少しはわかってる。残りはこれから浮かんでくるよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2140
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_bfef3931:

    # rin "I'm sure of it. I always have… reasons."
    rin "うん、きっとそうだ。私にはいつも……理由がある"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2142
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_22d6bd94:

    # "The ensuing silence kills Lilly's hopes all too visibly. That didn't last long."
    "その後に続く沈黙が、リリーの期待を完膚無きまでに打ち消してしまう。あっという間だったな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2144
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_c71f7ec7:

    # "Rin's, as far as I can tell unbased, assurances aside… what should be done?"
    "琳の――どうやら根拠のない――確信はともかく……どうすりゃいいんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2146
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_63c1b79c:

    # "We could just leave her to her own devices, whatever those are… but it's late and I don't think we'll be getting any thanks if Rin is found standing here in the middle of the night."
    "琳の目的がなんであれ、好きにさせて放っておくこともできる……でも、もう夜も遅いし、琳が夜中にここで突っ立っているのが見つかっても、それはそれでまずい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2148
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7891a198:

    # "Which she probably will, unless she manages to remember what she was doing here in the first place."
    "そもそもここで何をしていたのか思い出さない限り、きっと琳はここから動かないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2150
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a68dc945:

    # "As for me trying to guess what might've been going on in her mind when she decided to embark on this adventure, the chances seem to be on par with winning the lottery."
    "何を思って琳がこの冒険に乗り出そうとしたかを言い当てるとして、正解する確率は宝くじの一等を当てるのと同じくらいだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2152
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_516f0098:

    # "Several times in a row."
    "何回も連続で、だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2154
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_eefae812:

    # "Lilly is oddly quiet too. I'd appreciate some support from the sidelines here, especially if she's more familiar with Rin than I am."
    "リリーは妙に静かだ。もし俺より琳のことに詳しいんだったら、少しは助け船を出してくれるとありがたいんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2156
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_74fe4539:

    # "But it can't be helped. It seems her familiarity with Rin is exactly why she's staying subdued."
    "まあ、しょうがない。琳をよく知っているからこそ、リリーはおとなしくしているんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2158
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_77797ebf:

    # hi "So, I assume you were going somewhere, not coming back to the school… any idea where?"
    hi "それじゃあ、どこかに行こうとしてたんじゃないのか。学校に戻ろうとしてたわけじゃなさそうだし……どこか心当たりは？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2164
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a7229923:

    # "Her eyes widen in shock and she jolts back in a somewhat artificial way, making it seem like an act rehearsed for situations like this."
    "琳は何だかわざとらしくのけ反って、目を丸くする。そのせいで、こんな時のために演技を練習していたかのように見えてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2166
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_2f41bb09:

    # rin "Are you a mind reader? Is that your disability? How unique!"
    rin "君ってばエスパーなの？　それが君の障害？　すごいや！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2168
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7cd26fce:

    # hi "No… What? Why would you think that?"
    hi "ちが……何？　どこからそんな考えが出てくるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2174
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_73e1e6d8:

    # rin "You knew what I was doing."
    rin "私が何をしていたのか、知ってたじゃん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2179
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_430dbe8d:

    # hi "Eh, it was just an educated guess. We walked this same street in the other direction just before, to get to the store."
    hi "えっとな、ただの常識に基づいた推測だ。俺たちはコンビニに行くために、さっき同じ道を反対から来たんだから"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2181
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6676aade:

    # hi "If you were going to school, we would've met you on the way."
    hi "もし学校に向かってたなら、俺たちは途中で会ってたはずだろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2186
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_8cf3c02d:

    # rin "Oh."
    rin "ああ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2188
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d0fae6c4:

    # "She looks a little disappointed."
    "琳は少しがっかりしたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2190
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a7da7ad3:

    # "Like Kenji, Rin appears quick to jump to completely irrational conclusions."
    "健二みたいに、琳はすぐ訳のわからない結論に飛躍するらしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2192
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_849a9e34:

    # "Maybe it's something in the water here. I make a mental note to stock up on soft drinks."
    "ここの水には何か混ざってるのかもな。ジュースを買いだめしておこう、と心に刻む。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2194
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_0615cde1:

    # hi "You know, that is the second time this week that someone asked if I was a mind reader."
    hi "なあ、俺がエスパーかどうか聞いた人間は今週で二人目だぜ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2196
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_861657cf:

    # hi "Do I really give off that impression?"
    hi "俺、本当にそんな感じに見えるのか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2201
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6115b5ca:

    # "Rin shrugs her shoulders, which is all the answer I get."
    "琳は肩をすくめる。どっちなんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2203
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_9d9c33ab:

    # hi "You know—{w=0.3}{nw}"
    hi "あのな――{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2208
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ebe60555:

    # li "Maybe you should come with us back to the school?"
    li "琳さんも、私たちと一緒に学校に戻ったほうがいいんじゃありませんか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2210
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_4a8e77ad:

    # "Lilly interjects just as I am about to further debunk my alleged mind-reading capabilities. She sounds rather concerned, the paper-thin smile on her face badly disguising that fact."
    "俺がエスパー云々という誤解をきちんと解こうとしたところで、リリーが口を挟む。心配しているような口ぶりで、見え透いた笑顔はそのことをまったく隠せていない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2212
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_e4d03512:

    # "Maybe she came to the same conclusion as I did. For everyone's sake, I decide to let the mind-reading topic drop, as it's entirely inane anyway."
    "リリーは俺と同じ結論に達したのかもしれない。みんなのために、エスパーネタはこれでやめよう。どうせ意味なんてないんだし。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2214
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_0fc624fe:

    # hi "Yeah, Lilly's right. If you can't remember, there's no point staying here."
    hi "ああ、リリーの言うとおりだ。何も覚えてないんだったら、ここに居続ける必要はないだろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2219
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_372b6159:

    # "Rin considers this rather simple deduction for a moment, then nods."
    "琳はしばらくの間、このどちらかといえば簡単な理論を検討し、うなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2226
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "わかった"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2235
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_94271ed5:

    # "We start towards the school again, having wasted way more time than necessary with this episode."
    "俺たちは再び学校に向かって歩き出す。こんなことで必要以上に時間を無駄にしてしまった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2241
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_d364e472:

    # "Rin walks along the edge of the sidewalk in her arrhythmic way, looking like a mix of sleepwalker and rope dancer, while Lilly keeps one hand on my shoulder, tapping at the ground with her cane."
    "琳は歩道の端に沿ってふらふらと歩く。夢遊病者と綱渡り芸人が合わさったようだ。リリーは俺の肩に手をかけたまま、杖で地面を叩いている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2243
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_7dcaafb7:

    # "Tap step step tap tap step step step."
    "カツン、コツコツ、カツンカツン、コツコツコツ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2245
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_9cc78dc5:

    # "Apart from that and a few fragmented beginnings of conversation, it's quiet. A quiet quite apart from the relaxing one into town, at that."
    "その音と、とぎれとぎれの会話を除いては、あたりは静かだ。ただ、町の落ち着ける静けさとは全く別物だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2247
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_fb27c5a9:

    # hi "So how's the mural going?"
    hi "それで、壁画はうまくいってる？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2252
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ce07cf29:

    # rin "We are going to get bad luck. Never talk about works in progress."
    rin "縁起悪いなあ。完成前の作品のことは絶対話しちゃダメなんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2257
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_463bdc84:

    # li "I'm sure it'll be wonderful."
    li "きっとすばらしいものになると思いますよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2262
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_16515c32:

    # rin "Bad luck."
    rin "縁起悪い"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2264
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ac6d713c:

    # "Tap step tap step. She doesn't care to talk about it. Lilly's politeness feels out of place, for the first time. Step step step."
    "カツン、コツ、カツン、コツ。その話をしようともしない。はじめて、リリーの礼儀正しさが場違いな気がした。コツコツコツ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2266
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_669454a4:

    # "The hill Yamaku rests on top of is surprisingly steep, going uphill. We slow the pace, but I still feel my pulse rising and breathing getting heavier."
    "学園がたたずむ丘は驚くほど急だ。俺たちはペースを落とすけど、それでも自分の脈が上がり、息が辛くなっていくのを感じる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2268
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_40a667ed:

    # "Almost there, I can see the gates already."
    "あと少しだ。もう門は見えている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2270
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_2f153ac4:

    # "More than that, though, I notice that Lilly's hand slightly tightens on my shoulder. Interpreting it as a gesture that she wants to ask something, I speak up."
    "それに気を取られていても、肩に置かれたリリーの手が少しこわばるのがわかる。何かを聞きたがっているしぐさなのだと判断し、はっきりと言う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2272
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_53ebc339:

    # hi "Anything wrong, Lilly?"
    hi "リリー、どうかした？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2274
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_a4ebc6ac:

    # "I resist the urge to say 'Aside from our traveling companion?' But only just."
    "『そこの旅の仲間は別にしてだよ？』と、言ってしまいたい衝動をかろうじて抑える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2276
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_ffaa7054:

    # "For a moment she seems to debate whether she should even bring it up, but goes for it anyway."
    "一瞬、彼女は言い出そうか迷っているように見えた。けど、結局それを口にする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2281
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_af037596:

    # li "Is everything… all right?"
    li "大丈夫……ですか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2283
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_0d72664a:

    # hi "All right? How do you mean?"
    hi "大丈夫？　どういう意味？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2285
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_f79d9690:

    # "The fact I can't interpret her incredibly vague question puts her off, for a second."
    "あまりに遠回しで、わけがわからない。質問の意味が俺に伝わらなかったことで、リリーはわずかにたじろぐ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2287
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_26dbe909:

    # li "It's just… you seem unusually tired, I guess."
    li "いえ、ただ……ひどく疲れているようで"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2289
translate jp a1_friday_mind_your_step_6e21c5a8:

    # "Now that she brings it up, I notice that my breathing is strangely heavy. The uphill walk has really done a job on me."
    "そう言われて、自分の息がやけに荒くなっていることに気づく。上り坂にはほんとうにやられた。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2318
translate jp class_goes_lazily_03d06529:

    # "The class goes on lazily. I think I'm starting to get into the rhythm of the school."
    "だらだらと授業は進む。この学校のリズムにだんだん巻き込まれていく気がする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2320
translate jp class_goes_lazily_5d8a4c18:

    # "I have even stopped worrying about taking notes and being overtly attentive. The first days, I was pretty high-strung in class."
    "もうノートをとるとか授業に集中するとか、そういうことも気にしなくなった。最初の数日はかなり緊張していたからな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2322
translate jp class_goes_lazily_332b057d:

    # "Mutou finishes his lecture about electricity early, but continues without a pause about the festival."
    "武藤先生が電気に関する授業を早めに切り上げるが、間髪入れずに学園祭について話し始める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2327
translate jp class_goes_lazily_b032cdfb:

    # mu "So, as you know, the festival is on the day after tomorrow. I hope everyone's projects are going to be successful this year."
    mu "さて、知っての通り明後日は学園祭だ。お前たちの企画もうまくいくといいな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2332
translate jp class_goes_lazily_4526da28:

    # mu "Have a good time, but also come Sunday, please keep the meaning of this festival in your minds…"
    mu "当日の日曜は存分に楽しんでくれ。ただし忘れないで欲しいのは学園祭の意義、つまり……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2334
translate jp class_goes_lazily_b0169987:

    # mi "Games and fried food!"
    mi "ゲームと揚げ物！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2336
translate jp class_goes_lazily_515f270e:

    # "Everyone bursts out in laughter, and so do I."
    "俺もみんなも大笑いする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2341
translate jp class_goes_lazily_fa4aaac5:

    # mu "Yes, thank you Mikado."
    mu "そうだな、御門"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2346
translate jp class_goes_lazily_c14d1c29:

    # mu "But what I meant was more the—{w=.5}{nw}"
    mu "だが私が言いたいのはもっと――{w=.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2350
translate jp class_goes_lazily_68e54c91:

    # "The remainder of his sentence is buried beneath the ring of the lunch bells, and everyone starts packing their things."
    "その言葉の続きはお昼のチャイムに埋もれてしまい、みんな荷物を片付け始める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2352
translate jp class_goes_lazily_f562324f:

    # "Mutou deliberates for a moment, but since almost nobody seems to pay attention any more, he gives up and sits down."
    "先生はしばらく考え込むけど、もう誰も聞いていないので、あきらめて席に座る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2362
translate jp class_goes_lazily_9f7f451b:

    # "It's crowded in the hallway… or as crowded as hallways in this school probably get. Most of the students seem to be heading down for the cafeteria."
    "廊下は人でいっぱい……つまり、この学校にしては人でいっぱいだ。ほとんどの生徒は食堂に向かっているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2372
translate jp mas_doesnt_bother_447a18a1:

    # "Misha, and by proxy, Shizune, doesn't bother me for the entire morning."
    "ミーシャも静音も、午前中ずっと俺にちょっかいを出してこない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2376
translate jp mas_doesnt_bother_50cd6aa8:

    # "When the bell rings, I don't even look at the two of them as I walk out of the class."
    "チャイムが鳴ると、俺は二人のほうを見もせずに教室を出て行く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2384
translate jp mas_doesnt_bother_9f7f451b:

    # "It's crowded in the hallway… or as crowded as hallways in this school probably get. Most of the students seem to be heading down for the cafeteria."
    "廊下は人でいっぱい……つまり、この学校にしては人でいっぱいだ。ほとんどの生徒は食堂に向かっているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2389
translate jp a1c9o1_3ea0964d:

    # "What am I doing here?"
    "何やってんだよ、俺は？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2391
translate jp a1c9o1_0cc46f44:

    # "Am I really just going to fold and let Emi pull ahead?"
    "ここでへこたれて、笑美に引き離されておしまいなんて、そんなんでいいのかよ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2396
translate jp a1c9o1_d8e3a19a:

    # "I speed up."
    "俺はスピードを上げる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2398
translate jp a1c9o1_65410fd0:

    # "The second lap's done quickly, and without even considering it I keep going."
    "２周目を速く走りきり、何も考えずに走り続ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2400
translate jp a1c9o1_a17e70cb:

    # "Emi looks back over her shoulder at me and grins."
    "振り返った笑美が、俺を見てニコッと笑う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2405
translate jp a1c9o1_365caad0:

    # emi "Still going?"
    emi "まだやるの？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2407
translate jp a1c9o1_831657ae:

    # hi "Wouldn't *pant* want you *pant* to think I'm outta shape *pant*"
    hi "俺が……ハァ……不健康だとか……ハァ……思われたくないからね……ハァ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2419
translate jp a1c9o1_d113657e:

    # "Emi laughs - without breaking her stride, no less - and speeds up even more."
    "笑美は笑い――なのに少しもペースを乱さず――さらにスピードを上げていく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2421
translate jp a1c9o1_98573d5a:

    # "Well, if this is the way we're going to play things…"
    "ふん、そっちがそのつもりなら……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2423
translate jp a1c9o1_14d4ff19:

    # "I increase my own pace as well."
    "俺もペースを上げる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2425
translate jp a1c9o1_de2bbed5:

    # "I can feel my lungs burning, and my legs are starting to question just what the hell I think I'm doing."
    "肺が熱くなるのを感じる。脚が自分のしていることに不平を言い始める。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2427
translate jp a1c9o1_4e630424:

    # "Lactic acid screams in my muscles, but I close my ears."
    "乳酸が俺の筋肉の中で悲鳴を上げているけど、それには耳を貸さない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2429
translate jp a1c9o1_516c0c26:

    # "I can't let myself fall behind, because that would be a loss."
    "倒れるわけにはいかない、それは負けだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2431
translate jp a1c9o1_796ed81d:

    # "The rational voice in my head inquires mildly just when we started playing a game."
    "いつからこれは勝負になったんだ、と穏やかな理性の声が頭の中で問う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2433
translate jp a1c9o1_21a040f6:

    # "I'd answer it, but I'm having a lot of trouble thinking at present."
    "答えたいけど、今はまともにモノを考えることができない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2435
translate jp a1c9o1_f9a549b5:

    # "She's so {b}fast{/b}."
    "あいつ、{b}速すぎる{/b}。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2437
translate jp a1c9o1_e922115b:

    # "How the hell does she keep it—{w=.5}{nw}"
    "どうやってあんな速度を保っ――{w=.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2448
translate jp a1c9o1_97fdad25:

    # "It's like a string pulling at my chest, a choking feeling of narrowness and pain."
    "胸をひもで縛られたような、すさまじい息苦しさと痛み。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2450
translate jp a1c9o1_4d50c456:

    # "Before I can think of anything else than 'Oh shit,' the track disappears from under my feet."
    "『やばい』以外に何も考えられなくなる前に、自分の足元からトラックが消える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2457
translate jp a1c9o1_460b4e74:

    # "I stumble, one hand shooting down to clutch at my chest, the other hitting the track to keep me from falling on my face."
    "地面に倒れる。片手で胸をつかみ、もう片方の手を地に突いて、顔から落ちそうになるのを避ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2461
translate jp a1c9o1_036e9ebb:

    # "Emi whirls around and her eyes widen."
    "笑美が振り向き、目を丸くする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2463
translate jp a1c9o1_625a31b5:

    # emi "Hisao!"
    emi "久夫く――ん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2467
translate jp a1c9o1_90a6a720:

    # "She yells at me, sprinting from the other side of the track."
    "笑美は叫んで、トラックの反対側から走ってくる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2480
translate jp a1c9o1_edd6e03f:

    # emi "What's wrong?"
    emi "大丈夫？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2482
translate jp a1c9o1_3460499f:

    # hi "Nngh—Nothing, just…"
    hi "ぐっ――なんでもない、ちょっと……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2491
translate jp a1c9o1_776f2559:

    # "Keep your breathing steady."
    "呼吸を安定させるんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2493
translate jp a1c9o1_3e015e6d:

    # "Calm down. Don't panic."
    "落ち着け。慌てるな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2502
translate jp a1c9o1_2b12bba4:

    # "Don't panic."
    "慌てるな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2507
translate jp a1c9o1_3eccb6eb:

    # emi "Do you need me to get the nurse?"
    emi "ナースくん呼んだほうがいい？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2512
translate jp a1c9o1_ae955be5:

    # "I close my eyes, shutting out the outside world."
    "外の世界を遮ろうと、俺は目を閉じる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2530
translate jp a1c9o1_dfc1460e:

    # "My heart struggles to regain its rhythm."
    "心臓がリズムを取り戻そうと必死にもがく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2532
translate jp a1c9o1_37057dd6:

    # "Slowly, the pain in my chest begins to subside."
    "徐々に、胸の痛みが和らいでくる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2534
translate jp a1c9o1_03bd8e0d:

    # "Soon it's gone like nothing happened."
    "すぐに、痛みは何事もなかったかのように治まる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2536
translate jp a1c9o1_656de983:

    # "It was… nothing? No, something happened there."
    "何事もなかった……？　そんなはずはない、何かが起きたんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2544
translate jp a1c9o1_4bb250e0:

    # "I open my eyes again and glance at a very worried Emi."
    "目を開き、ちらりと笑美を見るととても心配そうにしている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2546
translate jp a1c9o1_8c6a4570:

    # hi "I think I'm fine."
    hi "大丈夫だと思うけどな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2548
translate jp a1c9o1_6863318e:

    # "My voice sounds weird even to myself, oddly even and matter-of-fact. It makes Emi frown."
    "俺の声は自分でも変に、奇妙なほど平坦に、無味乾燥に聞こえる。笑美はそれを聞いて眉をひそめる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2553
translate jp a1c9o1_9b4b05ec:

    # emi "I don't think you are."
    emi "そんなことないでしょ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2555
translate jp a1c9o1_60c2c468:

    # "She seems to come to a decision, and nods to herself."
    "笑美は何かを決心し、そしてうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2560
translate jp a1c9o1_e4911ffc:

    # emi "Right. You're coming with me."
    emi "そうだ。あたしと一緒に行こう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2562
translate jp a1c9o1_60e9c96f:

    # emi "You've got to see the nurse."
    emi "ナースくんに診てもらわなきゃ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2566
translate jp a1c9o1_c88be4d2:

    # "Emi grabs my arm and drags me up. I feel a bit wobbly, but I refuse the shoulder Emi offers for support."
    "笑美は俺の手をつかんで引っ張り上げる。俺は少しだけよろめくけど、笑美が貸そうとした肩を拒む。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2568
translate jp a1c9o1_38c387a7:

    # "Honestly, I'm a little ashamed by my own weakness."
    "正直なところ、俺は自分の弱さが少し恥ずかしい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2570
translate jp a1c9o1_26b2352c:

    # "I'd really rather not have Emi concerned about me, but it seems to be too late."
    "笑美に心配をかけたくなかったけど、どうやら遅すぎたようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2572
translate jp a1c9o1_f41cc967:

    # "Heck, I'd really rather not have anyone concerned about my condition, though at this point, it seems to be too late for that as well."
    "くそっ、誰にも俺の病気のことを心配されたくないのに、今となっては、それも手遅れのようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2574
translate jp a1c9o1_01aa0353:

    # "I'd like to be able to deal with the whole thing on my own, without being a bother to anyone else."
    "他人に迷惑をかけないで、なんでも自分でやっていけるようになりたい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2576
translate jp a1c9o1_cd66a7c6:

    # "While I'm wishing for things, I'd rather not have this condition in the first place."
    "色んなことを願ってはいるけど、そもそもこんな病気にかかっていなければ、と思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2589
translate jp a1c9o1_621bfcea:

    # emi "Nurse!"
    emi "ナースく―――ん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2591
translate jp a1c9o1_157426ee:

    # "Emi crashes into his office without knocking, but it doesn't alarm the nurse in the least."
    "笑美はノックもせずに医務室に押しかけるけど、ナースは少しも驚いた素振りを見せない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2598
translate jp a1c9o1_68003eda:

    # nk "Good morning, sunshine. What's up?"
    nk "おはよう、ひまわりちゃん。どうしたのかな？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2600
translate jp a1c9o1_0bc40dac:

    # "Sunshine? Anyway, he calmly sips from his coffee mug but lays it down after following Emi's gaze to me looming in the doorway."
    "ひまわりちゃんだって？　落ち着いたふうにマグカップのコーヒーを一口飲むナースだが、笑美の視線をたどって、入り口にぬっと現れた俺の姿を確認すると、マグカップを置く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2605
translate jp a1c9o1_06ad722e:

    # nk "Hisao? What brings you here?"
    nk "久夫くんだね？　なんの用かな？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2610
translate jp a1c9o1_6f4444ae:

    # emi "We were running and he stumbled over and started grabbing at his chest and I thought I'd come get you and make him wait there but he said he was okay but then I thought you should see him anyway and—{w=1.5}{nw}"
    emi "一緒に走ってたら久夫くんが転んで、それから胸を押さえだしたからあたしナースくんを呼んでこようと思って、けど久夫くんが大丈夫だって言ってでもあたしはナースくんに見せたほうがいいと思ってそれで――{w=1.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2615
translate jp a1c9o1_efea55c6:

    # nk "Easy there, Emi. Calm down."
    nk "大丈夫だよ、笑美ちゃん。落ち着いて"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2620
translate jp a1c9o1_501439a1:

    # nk "Hisao, what happened?"
    nk "久夫くん、何があったのかな？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2622
translate jp a1c9o1_80b4814d:

    # hi "I don't know. We were running, and then my chest started hurting like that time before, but it went away after a few seconds."
    hi "わかりません。二人でランニングしてたら、以前みたいに胸が痛くなり始めたんだけど、ほんの数秒で治まりました"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2624
translate jp a1c9o1_e9cf4eae:

    # hi "It was just a flutter or something."
    hi "ただの粗動か何かですよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2629
translate jp a1c9o1_99b21d37:

    # "The nurse frowns, as if to say that 'just a flutter' is some kind of oxymoron."
    "ナースは、『ただの粗動』というのは矛盾しているぞと言い出しそうな、難しい顔をする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2631
translate jp a1c9o1_fe7c7b2f:

    # nk "I didn't mean quite this when I suggested to get some exercise. You've got to be more careful, Hisao."
    nk "少し運動をするようにとは言ったけど、こんなことになるまでやれと言ったつもりはないよ。もっと気をつけないと、久夫くん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2633
translate jp a1c9o1_2926a610:

    # hi "I was being careful, I just…"
    hi "注意はしてましたよ、俺はただ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2635
translate jp a1c9o1_1d53dd82:

    # "Come to think of it, 'I just got into a race with a member of the track team' doesn't seem as well reasoned as I thought it would."
    "考えてみると、『俺はただ陸上部の部員と競争してたんです』なんてのは思ったほど筋が通ってない言い訳だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2637
translate jp a1c9o1_e5c9caae:

    # nk "You just what?"
    nk "ただなんだい？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2639
translate jp a1c9o1_a2de4103:

    # hi "Er… that is…"
    hi "あ……あの時は……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2641
translate jp a1c9o1_f25a70d1:

    # hi "I was racing Emi."
    hi "笑美と競争してたんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2643
translate jp a1c9o1_7180a7c7:

    # nk "Emi, is this true?"
    nk "笑美ちゃん、それは本当かい？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2648
translate jp a1c9o1_e5f8771c:

    # "Emi fidgets, looking adorably contrite."
    "笑美はそわそわする。悔いるような表情がまたかわいい。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2650
translate jp a1c9o1_1ddbef16:

    # emi "Um, well…"
    emi "えっと、あの……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2655
translate jp a1c9o1_a13ebad7:

    # "Finally she can't seem to bring herself to say it aloud, and merely nods."
    "結局、笑美は言葉にすることができず、ただ単にうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2657
translate jp a1c9o1_d46deda5:

    # "The nurse sighs and rubs at his forehead with one hand tiredly."
    "ナースは、やれやれとため息をつくと、疲れたように自分の額を手でこする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2659
translate jp a1c9o1_bc4c58da:

    # nk "Emi, you've got to be more sensitive to the limits of others!"
    nk "笑美ちゃん、他人の限度ってものにもっと気を遣わなきゃダメじゃないか！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2661
translate jp a1c9o1_d366fff5:

    # nk "I don't know if he told you, but Hisao has a bad heart, and getting him to race you was incredibly irresponsible."
    nk "久夫くんが君に話したか知らないけど、彼は心臓が悪いんだよ。競争に誘うなんてあまりに無責任だよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2663
translate jp a1c9o1_6fc21b5f:

    # hi "Er, actually I started it."
    hi "あー、それ本当は俺が始めたんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2665
translate jp a1c9o1_7944d6fe:

    # "The nurse is stunned by my statement."
    "ナースは俺の発言に唖然となる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2667
translate jp a1c9o1_78d3c419:

    # nk "You WHAT?"
    nk "なんだって？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2669
translate jp a1c9o1_f1bbe428:

    # hi "We were just running, and Emi started to pull away, and so I uh, sped up to catch her."
    hi "僕ら、ランニングやってて、それで笑美に引き離され始めて、それで、あの、追いつこうとしてスピード上げたんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2671
translate jp a1c9o1_de8b2076:

    # "The nurse stares at the ceiling, mutters a prayer for patience to some god or another, and looks back down at the both of us."
    "ナースは天井をじっと見つめ、落ち着くために神様か何かに祈りの言葉をつぶやいてから、俺たち二人に視線を戻す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2673
translate jp a1c9o1_2aa31621:

    # nk "So you're {b}both{/b} stupid."
    nk "じゃあ君らは{b}二人とも{/b}大バカだってことか"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2675
translate jp a1c9o1_3cd08ef6:

    # nk "That's a comfort, I guess."
    nk "それがせめてもの救いだな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2677
translate jp a1c9o1_e1d14599:

    # nk "Now come on, Hisao. I've got to make sure your heart's not going to explode or something."
    nk "こっちにおいで、久夫くん。君の心臓が爆発とかしないか確認しないとね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2687
translate jp a1c9o1_d825016a:

    # "I dutifully obey and follow him to the adjacent room where we ascertain that I am, in fact, not going to keel over and die."
    "俺は律儀にナースの指示に従って、要は、卒倒して死んだりしないかどうかを確かめるために隣の部屋へとついて行く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2689
translate jp a1c9o1_279c4841:

    # nk "So how does it feel?"
    nk "で、調子はどうだい？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2691
translate jp a1c9o1_bd678f26:

    # hi "I don't know. Nothing much. Tired, but it might be just from the exercise."
    hi "わかりません。大したことはないです。疲れてますけど、さっきの運動のせいかも"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2693
translate jp a1c9o1_da0b329d:

    # nk "You should stay here for a few hours and rest, and we'll see how you feel after that."
    nk "少しの間ここで休んだほうがいい、後でまた様子を見よう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2695
translate jp a1c9o1_482dddc6:

    # "I am not going to object, so I lie down on the infirmary bed."
    "ここでナースに逆らうつもりはない。俺は医務室のベッドの上で横になる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2702
translate jp a1c9o1_58ef32c4:

    # "A thoroughly miserable Emi comes in after getting an earful from the nurse in the other room."
    "その後、隣の部屋でナースにお説教を食らってすっかり落ち込んだ笑美がやって来る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2704
translate jp a1c9o1_88684818:

    # "I couldn't hear what he said through the closed door, but I'm sure it wasn't pleasantries."
    "閉じられたドア越しにナースが何を言ってるのか、俺には聞こえなかったけど、愉快な冗談じゃなかったってことは確かだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2711
translate jp a1c9o1_283870b6:

    # emi "Look, I'm really, really sorry."
    emi "ねえ、ホントに、ホントにごめんね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2713
translate jp a1c9o1_52111694:

    # emi "I should've been more careful."
    emi "あたしがもっと気をつけてればよかったのに"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2715
translate jp a1c9o1_3b5f3e2f:

    # hi "Hey, you didn't know. It's not your fault."
    hi "どうして、君は知らなかったんだろ。君のせいじゃないよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2717
translate jp a1c9o1_ccee5ddf:

    # "She looks awfully down and sorry, and my reassurances don't do anything much to cheer her up."
    "ひどく落ち込んで申し訳なさそうにしている彼女には、俺の元気づけの言葉は大した励ましにもならない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2719
translate jp a1c9o1_9014babc:

    # emi "I want to make it up to you."
    emi "埋め合わせさせてくれないかな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2721
translate jp a1c9o1_2a981ea5:

    # "Again with that decisive nod."
    "もう一度、決心して頷く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2726
translate jp a1c9o1_b0b8170d:

    # emi "So you have to come to lunch with me."
    emi "だからあたしと一緒にお昼食べようよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2728
translate jp a1c9o1_12413956:

    # emi "I'll bring it for you, okay? Something really really good!"
    emi "あたしお昼持ってくるから、ね？　すっごくすっごくおいしいお弁当！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2730
translate jp a1c9o1_bdab6a9e:

    # "I start with a 'You don't have to…' but then shut up and just nod at her when I see her face."
    "『いいよ、そんな……』と言いかけたけど、笑美の表情を見て俺は黙って頷く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2735
translate jp a1c9o1_ff8dd477:

    # emi "Good!"
    emi "よかったぁ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2740
translate jp a1c9o1_87c67ad4:

    # emi "We meet on the roof."
    emi "屋上で待ち合わせね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2742
translate jp a1c9o1_be2d8009:

    # hi "We?"
    hi "待ち合わせ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2747
translate jp a1c9o1_946bd597:

    # emi "Yep! The weather's nice now, so the roof's a great spot for lunch, you know."
    emi "そうだよ！　今なら天気も良いし、屋上はお昼食べるには絶好の場所なんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2749
translate jp a1c9o1_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "確かにな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2754
translate jp a1c9o1_06621ec7:

    # emi "You'll come, right?"
    emi "来てくれるでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2756
translate jp a1c9o1_45d67c99:

    # emi "You wouldn't deny me the chance to make it up to you?"
    emi "あたしに埋め合わせさせてくれるよね？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2758
translate jp a1c9o1_f73e23a7:

    # hi "Of course not."
    hi "当然だろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2763
translate jp a1c9o1_10ffbe01:

    # emi "Great! See you there!"
    emi "よかった！　じゃあまた屋上でね！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2770
translate jp a1c9o1_6ff077f7:

    # "I stay afloat somewhere between asleep and awake, feeling completely drained."
    "俺は完全に疲れ果て、眠りと目覚めの間をふわふわと漂い続ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2772
translate jp a1c9o1_4e7cbb1e:

    # "Not only my body, but all of me is limp and paralyzed, apart from my senses."
    "体だけじゃなく俺の全部が――意識をのぞいて――ぐったりとなって麻痺している。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2774
translate jp a1c9o1_e9de47da:

    # "I swallow with difficulty and then try to lie as still as I can, which in this state is not a very hard thing to do."
    "俺はなんとか唾を飲み込み、ベッドに横になったままできるだけ体を動かさないようにする。今の俺の状態ならそんなに難しいことじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2776
translate jp a1c9o1_c0112e72:

    # "The nurse is shuffling around on the other side of the curtains he drew to give me privacy. I can see his shadow shifting about in the sunlight."
    "俺のために引いたカーテンの向こう側で、ナースはすり足で歩き回る。太陽の光の中で影が動くのが見える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2778
translate jp a1c9o1_29ab6a6c:

    # "He has opened the window of his office. It's windy outside."
    "ナースが医務室の窓を開けていた。外は風が強い。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2780
translate jp a1c9o1_7496323b:

    # "The clean white curtains flutter in the breeze in a heavy, lazy motion, like waves. Light sifts through them slowly, half absorbing into the fabric."
    "綺麗な白いカーテンが、重くのろのろとした調子で、さざ波のようにそよ風にパタパタとはためく。陽の光は自らの半分をカーテンの布地に吸い込まれながらも、ゆっくりとその篩を通り抜けてくる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2787
translate jp a1c9o1_77a919e1:

    # "I close my eyes. The breeze on my face feels like the soft fabric of the curtains."
    "俺は目を閉じる。顔に当たるそよ風がカーテンの柔らかい布のようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2789
translate jp a1c9o1_83fdc0bd:

    # "I listen to the sound of my heartbeat for a moment, trying to shut out the sound of the nurse tapping away on his computer, and my own heavy breathing."
    "ナースがパソコンのキーボードを打つ音や、自分の荒い息づかいを遮断しながら、自分の心臓の鼓動に耳を集中させる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2791
translate jp a1c9o1_a321482d:

    # "It's steady."
    "規則的だな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2793
translate jp a1c9o1_f11cda68:

    # "Damn it, not even a week and I end up like this again. I really screwed up this time. Should've known better than to play the half-baked sports star in front of a real one."
    "ちきしょう、まだ１週間も経ってないってのにまたこんなことになっちまった。今回のはマジで大失敗だ。 半端なスポーツ選手ごっこなんてやるんじゃなかった。それも本物の選手を前にして。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2795
translate jp a1c9o1_8ddb479f:

    # "And why did I try to act brave, like that heart flutter was no big deal, even when it was obvious that it was?"
    "どうして粗動が大したことじゃないなんて、かっこつけようとしたんだ。明らかに大問題じゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2797
translate jp a1c9o1_d24d8bf6:

    # "It was just a reflex, to push it away, to keep it inside."
    "反射的な行動だったんだ。現実から目を背けて、隠しておこうとするための。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2799
translate jp a1c9o1_d519b8d4:

    # "I didn't want it to happen."
    "こんなこと起きて欲しくなかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2801
translate jp a1c9o1_d373b1ee:

    # "I didn't want Emi to see it."
    "笑美に見られたくなかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2803
translate jp a1c9o1_8b6af460:

    # "Aaah…"
    "あぁぁぁ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2805
translate jp a1c9o1_a5c55da1:

    # "Stupidstupidstupid."
    "馬鹿だ馬鹿だ馬鹿だ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2807
translate jp a1c9o1_0556f8bc:

    # "I have to be more careful, or I will end up in the hospital again, or worse."
    "もっと気をつけなきゃ。そうじゃなきゃ、また病院に逆戻りだ。さもなきゃ、もっとひどいことに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2809
translate jp a1c9o1_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2811
translate jp a1c9o1_aa6ee906:

    # "That's my final thought before I give in to the tiredness."
    "疲労感に音を上げる前の、最後の思考だった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2823
translate jp a1c9o1_1cb96d17:

    # "I fell asleep. For how long? What time is it?"
    "眠っていた。どのくらい寝た？　今何時なんだ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2825
translate jp a1c9o1_674e790e:

    # "I'm feeling a little lightheaded and I keep blinking compulsively."
    "少し頭がクラクラして、耐えられずまばたきを繰り返す。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2830
translate jp a1c9o1_4dac7f96:

    # "Pushing the curtain aside, I squint my eyes against the unfiltered light pouring in from the window. The texture of the canvas feels nothing like the wind did before."
    "カーテンを脇によせ、窓から直接降り注いでくる光に目を細める。キャンバス布の手触りは、前に感じた風とは似ても似つかない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2832
translate jp a1c9o1_b00cdb53:

    # "The nurse looks up from his work, sitting exactly where he was before."
    "さっきと全く同じ場所に座っていたナースが、机から顔を上げる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2837
translate jp a1c9o1_6854034a:

    # nk "How are you feeling?"
    nk "調子はどうかな？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2839
translate jp a1c9o1_f806d055:

    # "I can't really tell, so I don't answer anything. I'm feeling kinda groggy from falling asleep at such a weird time, hopefully I don't look too weird."
    "自分でもよくわからなかったので、何も答えない。こんな変な時間に寝てしまったので、意識がぼんやりしている。変な風に見えないといいんだけど。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2841
translate jp a1c9o1_8de7cfd0:

    # hi "What time is it?"
    hi "何時ですか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2843
translate jp a1c9o1_4a62b305:

    # "Me croaking the question to gain some orientation. The nurse looking at his wristwatch before answering."
    "状況を把握しようと、しゃがれ声で尋ねる。ナースは質問に答える前に腕時計を見る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2845
translate jp a1c9o1_2074f849:

    # "Things seem to happen in slow motion."
    "スローモーションみたいに感じる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2850
translate jp a1c9o1_1d22087d:

    # nk "Quarter past ten."
    nk "１０時１５分"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2852
translate jp a1c9o1_5b69b7a9:

    # "I try to think for a moment what that means but I'm not really sure."
    "それが何を意味するのか少し考えるけど、よくわからない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2857
translate jp a1c9o1_3ecec8b7:

    # nk "You didn't answer my question, Hisao."
    nk "僕の質問に答えてないよ、久夫くん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2859
translate jp a1c9o1_1f001b1e:

    # hi "Oh. Fine."
    hi "ああ、大丈夫です"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2864
translate jp a1c9o1_f98191a9:

    # nk "Climb down from that bed then, and let’s see how you are doing. Don’t…"
    nk "じゃあベッドから降りて、様子を見よう。でもあまり……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2882
translate jp a1c9o1_306b85b8:

    # "I try to do exactly that, only to sway dizzily when I move too fast. The nurse moves to support me by an arm and sighs."
    "言われた通りにしようとするけど、早く動きすぎて、ただフラフラと倒れこんでしまう。ナースが俺の腕を取って支え、ため息をつく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2889
translate jp a1c9o1_ee281343:

    # nk "…stand up too quickly, is what I was going to say. Just sit there, I’ll check your pressure to make sure."
    nk "……あまり急いで起きなくていい、って言おうとしたんだよ。そこに座って、確認のために血圧を測るからね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2893
translate jp a1c9o1_3c4e3160:

    # "My good intentions sure lasted for a long time. I shut up, embarrassed with myself, while the nurse gets busy with an old-fashioned contraption and my arm. After a couple of minutes, he puts it away, looking neither pleased nor unhappy."
    "俺のやることはずっと裏目に出続けている。ナースが古めかしい血圧計と俺の腕を取って忙しくしている間、きまりの悪さを感じながら黙る。 数分後、ナースは血圧計をしまう。その表情は不満そうでも満足そうでもない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2898
translate jp a1c9o1_dfdde33b:

    # nk "You’re all right. Head stopped spinning?"
    nk "問題はなさそうだ。頭のふらつきは治まったかい？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2900
translate jp a1c9o1_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2902
translate jp a1c9o1_e01870ad:

    # nk "Good. And how are the contents doing?"
    nk "よし。じゃあ中身のほうはどうだい？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2907
translate jp a1c9o1_aba55eb0:

    # nk "You didn’t show very good judgment out there, Hisao."
    nk "君の行動は軽率だったね、久夫くん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2909
translate jp a1c9o1_51a6b41f:

    # "I swallow the retort I was going to make. It’s what I was thinking myself, but hearing it stated by somebody else makes me want to protest."
    "反論しそうになったけど、その言葉を飲み込む。俺だってそう思っていた。でも同じことを他人から聞かされると言い返したくなる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2911
translate jp a1c9o1_7cf618fd:

    # "What he’s saying is not pleasant to hear. Doesn’t make him any less right."
    "ナースの言っていることは不愉快だ。それでも正しいことには変わりない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2913
translate jp a1c9o1_146eaf2c:

    # hi "No, sir."
    hi "はい"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2918
translate jp a1c9o1_cd6028f4:

    # "He nods, still looking as neutral as he was before."
    "彼は頷く。相変わらずよくわからない表情。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2920
translate jp a1c9o1_eff49640:

    # "It would be easy to be angry at him if he said 'Told you so' or something, but he doesn’t."
    "もし『言わんこっちゃない』とか言ってくれたら、俺だって簡単に怒れる。でもナースはそんなことは言わない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2922
translate jp a1c9o1_7ded1b64:

    # nk "I can try and help you to keep your health, but ultimately the last call lies with you. Hopefully this little episode will be something that’ll remind you of that."
    nk "僕は君の健康を維持する手助けはできる。でも最後に責任を持つのは君なんだよ。これに懲りて、そのことを覚えていてくれるといいんだけどね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2927
translate jp a1c9o1_dbc481dd:

    # nk "Here, a note for your teacher. To avoid an interrogation."
    nk "ほら、先生に渡すメモだ。質問責めに会わないためのね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2929
translate jp a1c9o1_87b27ccb:

    # "I take the slip of paper he's offering and then make my leave as I can't think of anything else to say, nor even really want to."
    "俺はナースがくれた紙切れを受け取り、そのまま医務室を後にする。言うことなんて何も思いつかなかったし、そもそも何も言いたくなかった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2934
translate jp a1c9o1_f4a130ed:

    # nk "Stay out of trouble, you hear me? I don't think it was anything but a scare, but next time could be different."
    nk "面倒ごとは避けるんだよ、聞いてるかい？　今回は怖い目にあったくらいで済んだけど、次は違うかもしれないからね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2936
translate jp a1c9o1_3aa97bb5:

    # "I hear you."
    "聞いてますよ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2943
translate jp a1c9o1_84ebdef1:

    # "There is some way to get to the school building straight from the auxiliary building, but I'm not keen to find out and possibly get lost, so I go out from the exit that I know works."
    "副校舎から本校舎にまっすぐ向かう方法があるそうだけど、そんなに見つけたいとも思わないし、迷う可能性だってあるから、確実に出られるとわかっている出入口から外に出る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2948
translate jp a1c9o1_a1872af1:

    # "I stop at the stairs of the auxiliary building, deliberating for a moment between going to the dorms to get my books and stuff and going straight away to the class."
    "副校舎の階段で足を止め、教科書などを取りに寮に立ち寄るか、速攻で学校に向かうかを考える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2950
translate jp a1c9o1_21c816d8:

    # "The sun stings my eyes, so I head towards the dorms."
    "太陽の光が目にしみるので、俺は寮へと向かう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2957
translate jp a1c9o2_0236f9a5:

    # "I let Emi go with her own pace, and she doesn't show mercy, pulling half a lap ahead of me in an instant."
    "好きに走ればいいさ。笑美は容赦なく、すぐに半周差をつける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2959
translate jp a1c9o2_3f13fb51:

    # "I don't blame her."
    "別に腹は立たない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2961
translate jp a1c9o2_af98cbd8:

    # "I mean, it's not as if I'm really putting up any sort of real fight out here, is it?"
    "というか、別に本気で勝負してるわけじゃないし。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2963
translate jp a1c9o2_8233baea:

    # "Instead, I'm just running at a steady pace, which is what I should be doing, right?"
    "かわりに、俺は一定のペースで走っている。本来はこうすべきだろ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2965
translate jp a1c9o2_0036a9bc:

    # "There's no need to go pushing my limits at this stage of the game."
    "ここで自分の限界に挑戦する必要なんてない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2967
translate jp a1c9o2_c778f344:

    # "God, is this even worth it?"
    "ちくしょう、こんなことして意味あるのかよ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2972
translate jp a1c9o2_7bf82133:

    # "As we finish the second lap, I break off again."
    "２周目を走り終えると同時に、俺はまた途中でやめる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2974
translate jp a1c9o2_df4b275e:

    # "Emi keeps going, and it almost seems to me that she's disappointed."
    "笑美はそのまま走り続けてるけど、なんだかがっかりしているようでもある。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2976
translate jp a1c9o2_e4f26bfe:

    # "Well, that's stupid."
    "いや、それはないな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2978
translate jp a1c9o2_369be0e6:

    # "I don't have anything to prove to her - come to think of it, I've got nothing to prove to myself, either."
    "笑美に誇れるものなんて俺には何もない――考えてみれば、自分自身に誇れるものだって持ってないんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2980
translate jp a1c9o2_d65ad35b:

    # "I'm just fine the way I am."
    "別に俺はこのままでいいさ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2982
translate jp a1c9o2_8e3c4d34:

    # "And what I'm not is a runner."
    "それに俺は陸上選手になるためにやってんじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2984
translate jp a1c9o2_ad9cfa10:

    # "This was probably a bad idea."
    "こんなこと始めなければ良かったな。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2986
translate jp a1c9o2_b946a9da:

    # "Maybe there's something else I can do instead of this."
    "かわりに何か他のことができるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2988
translate jp a1c9o2_ae6f5727:

    # "Getting up this early sucks, anyway. There's got to be some other way to keep healthy."
    "それに、こんなに早く起きるのはイヤだ。健康を保つ方法は他にもあるはずだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2990
translate jp a1c9o2_9fcb4df6:

    # "Walking, maybe. Nice afternoon walks."
    "ウォーキングなんていいかもな。快適な午後の散歩。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2992
translate jp a1c9o2_7b993831:

    # "Yeah, that sounds good. Running isn't for me."
    "ああ、それが良さそうだ。ランニングは俺には合ってない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:2999
translate jp a1c9o2_457978d9:

    # "I wave to Emi and head back to my room."
    "俺は笑美に手を振り、自分の部屋に戻る。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3001
translate jp a1c9o2_674330d9:

    # "I'll think of something else later."
    "後で別の方法でも考えるか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3006
translate jp a1c10o1_ca0a164b:

    # hi "It's nothing."
    hi "なんでもない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3011
translate jp a1c10o1_b6aa72c4:

    # "I quickly step in front of them, trying to hide the stuff behind my back. Shizune takes a step back, looking suspicious, but it's an expression not without concern."
    "俺は素早く二人の前に立って、薬を背中で隠そうとする。静音は怪訝そうな表情で一歩退く。でもその表情には心配も混じっている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3013
translate jp a1c10o1_7b29f7fa:

    # "I hope if I avoid it, she'll understand that I don't want her to keep prodding me about it."
    "このまま話題を避ければ、詮索されたくないということが静音に伝わるんじゃないかと期待する。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3018
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3023
translate jp a1c10o1_1a62c997:

    # mi "Really? What are you hiding, Hicchan~?"
    mi "ほんとに？　なに隠してるの、ひっちゃん～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3025
translate jp a1c10o1_f48a475f:

    # hi "Nothing."
    hi "なんでもない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3030
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3035
translate jp a1c10o1_2489eb65:

    # mi "Is that so~?"
    mi "そーなの～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3037
translate jp a1c10o1_55daedf0:

    # "I realize I can't really squirm my way out of this. They are nosy by nature and hiding it is just going to pique their curiosity more."
    "こんなやりかたじゃ話題を変えるのは無理だと気づく。もともと二人とも詮索好きなんだし、隠したって好奇心をかき立てるだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3039
translate jp a1c10o1_86d95e35:

    # hi "Yeah okay, it is {b}something{/b}, but I don't really want to talk about it, okay? Not… yet."
    hi "わかったよもう、確かになんでもなくはないよ。でもこのことはあまり話したくないんだ……まだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3041
translate jp a1c10o1_cc2c765d:

    # hi "Can we just put this aside for now?"
    hi "今は触れないでおいてくれないか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3046
translate jp a1c10o1_44ef421c:

    # "As Misha translates, Shizune stares at me hard with her eyes focused and analytical as ever, peering at me curiously over the rims of her glasses."
    "ミーシャが通訳すると、静音はいつも以上に見透かすような目つきでこちらを見据える。眼鏡の縁越しに、好奇心に満ちた視線で見つめられる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3048
translate jp a1c10o1_a8ec7973:

    # "Her fingers press against each other thoughtfully, as if she's weighing the value of pursuing this further than necessary against the insult of disrespecting my wish."
    "熟慮するように両手を合わせる。俺の意志を無視する失礼なことだとしても、このまま問いただす価値があるのか考えているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3050
translate jp a1c10o1_0977cd4a:

    # "Her expression finally melts into a slight smile and she signs something to Misha."
    "ようやく静音は表情を和らげてかすかに笑い、ミーシャに何事か手話で伝える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3057
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3062
translate jp a1c10o1_fbc26a12:

    # mi "Okay~! Then, we'll wait, and become better and better friends, and one day when you feel like it, you can tell us about it~!"
    mi "おっけ～！　じゃあ、わたしたち待つよ。これからずっとずっと仲良くなって、ひっちゃんが話したくなったら、そのときはわたしたちに教えてね！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3064
translate jp a1c10o1_e3cd9213:

    # "Both of them smile widely at me, and I feel shocked and a little stupid about being like this."
    "二人ともにっこりと笑う。俺はショックだった。こんな態度をとった自分がなんだかバカみたいだと思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3066
translate jp a1c10o1_5c248407:

    # "They are not stupid, and probably can at least halfway guess what's going on with me. And…"
    "この二人はバカじゃない。俺の事情だって半分は見当がついているはずだ。それに……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3068
translate jp a1c10o1_480840fc:

    # "Such simple, kind words. I feel relieved that they don't think any worse of me even if I'm like this. Even if I'm not like the rest here. Even if I can't be at ease about it."
    "こんなに無邪気で、優しい言葉。二人が全く気にしないでくれたことに心が軽くなる。 俺のこんな態度を見ても、俺が山久の他のみんなと同じでなくても、俺自身がそれを受け入れられていなくても。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3070
translate jp a1c10o1_650ffc23:

    # "Seems that behind the obnoxious, mischievous acts, both of these girls are really kind and good people. That's what I think."
    "憎たらしい、いたずらじみたことをするけど、本当はとても優しくていい子たちなんだ。俺はそう思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3072
translate jp a1c10o1_9d5a9627:

    # hi "Thanks."
    hi "ありがとう"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3074
translate jp a1c10o1_d05d0094:

    # hi "So, you want me to help you out today, right? Since I'm one of you now?"
    hi "で、俺になんか手伝って欲しいんだろ？　もう俺もお前らの仲間ってわけだし"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3079
translate jp a1c10o1_f7267e24:

    # mi "Yup~!"
    mi "うん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3081
translate jp a1c10o1_10d0567b:

    # hi "After class?"
    hi "放課後？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3086
translate jp a1c10o1_37f9b18a:

    # mi "No no no~! Now!"
    mi "ちがうちが～う！　今すぐだよ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3088
translate jp a1c10o1_b22b67f6:

    # hi "Now? But what about class? You are going to skip again?"
    hi "今？　って、授業はどうすんだよ？　またさぼる気か？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3093
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3098
translate jp a1c10o1_1fe3ef4f:

    # mi "Hahaha~! It's for the common good, so we sacrifice our math lessons, and maybe the social studies too~!"
    mi "ははは～！　これは公共の利益のためなのよ、だから数学の授業には犠牲になってもらうの。もしかしたら、社会もね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3100
translate jp a1c10o1_04d5b018:

    # hi "Well, I guess I'm fine with it."
    hi "そっか。まあ、俺は構わないけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3105
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3110
translate jp a1c10o1_e55789ff:

    # mi "Awesome, Hicchan~! You said it, okay? Remember: 'I'm fine with helping out~,' that's what you said, right~?"
    mi "そうこなくっちゃ、ひっちゃん～！　今自分で言ったよね？　忘れちゃだめよ！　『俺は手伝っても構わないけど』って、そういうことだよね、ね～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3112
translate jp a1c10o1_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3114
translate jp a1c10o1_b72d50ad:

    # "That tone… I suddenly regret saying it."
    "その声の調子……俺は突然自分の言葉を後悔する。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3119
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3124
translate jp a1c10o1_d85a9d8a:

    # mi "Okay~! Are you ready to go then? We can go to the office together~!"
    mi "おっけ～！　じゃあ用意はいい？　生徒会室に一緒にいこ～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3126
translate jp a1c10o1_11cb8f39:

    # hi "No. You're probably going to make me carry all your stuff for you or something."
    hi "いや待て。俺に荷物全部持たせるとか、何か仕掛ける気だろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3131
translate jp a1c10o1_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3136
translate jp a1c10o1_8fd7521b:

    # mi "Don't be silly, Hicchan."
    mi "何バカなこと言ってるの、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3141
translate jp a1c10o1_5b646c2c:

    # mi "We've never walked to school together, Hicchan~."
    mi "わたしたち、一度も一緒に登校したことなかったじゃん、ひっちゃん～"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3143
translate jp a1c10o1_0003e7fa:

    # "I almost want to ask why we would, but then it dawns on me. The both of them consider me their friend, like Misha said before. And they want to become better friends with me, even."
    "なぜ一緒に登校しなきゃいけないのか、という問いがのどまで出かかる。でもふと俺は気づく。 二人とも俺を友達だと思ってくれているんだ。さっきミーシャが言ったように。そしてもっと仲良くなりたいんだ、と。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3145
translate jp a1c10o1_27eed762:

    # "It's weird, I've never really thought about them that way. Or any of the people I've met so far this week. Is it really so easy?"
    "妙な感じだ。二人のことを、いや今週会った人たちの誰であれ、そんな風に考えたことなんてなかった。そんなにあっさりと打ち解けるものなんだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3147
translate jp a1c10o1_5c3bff2b:

    # "Just like that…"
    "いとも簡単に……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3149
translate jp a1c10o1_40abaef0:

    # hi "Okay, let's go, then."
    hi "わかった。じゃあ行くか"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3154
translate jp a1c10o1_f4aa0636:

    # "Shizune grins craftily and puts her hands behind her back."
    "静音は何か企んでいるような笑顔を浮かべると、両手を背中にまわす。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3159
translate jp a1c10o1_734b4f43:

    # mi "Hahaha~! That's great, Hicchan~! Okay, okay, but first~! You had a really great idea, Shicchan liked it a lot… So~! it's time for a game!"
    mi "ははは～！　ありがと、ひっちゃん～！　おっけおっけ、でもその前に～！　今のすごくいいアイディアだね、しっちゃんも気に入ってるよ……なので～！　今からゲームしよう！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3161
translate jp a1c10o1_c0658d3e:

    # hi "Oh no."
    hi "おいマジかよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3166
translate jp a1c10o1_ebd32f1a:

    # mi "Shicchan is holding a 1000-yen note in one hand, Hicchan~! If you guess which one, you can have it! If you don't…"
    mi "しっちゃんは片手に千円札を持ってるよ～！　どっちの手か当てられたら、ひっちゃんが千円ゲット～！　はずしたら……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3171
translate jp a1c10o1_ca99c1b4:

    # mi "You're carrying all our books to school~! Right, Shicchan~? Right~!"
    mi "わたしたちの荷物、全部学校まで持っていってね～！　だよね、しっちゃん～？　ね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3173
translate jp a1c10o1_1ed8e2a8:

    # "She and Shizune exchange nods."
    "ミーシャと静音はうなずきあう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3178
translate jp a1c10o1_e8c36b8b:

    # mi "Okay, Hicchan~! Get ready~!"
    mi "おっけー、ひっちゃん～！　覚悟してね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3185
translate jp a1c10o1_8895c6ea:

    # "Carrying three bags instead of one, I think about the day that's ahead of me. Of us."
    "かばん一つじゃなくて、かばん三つ。俺は今日これからのことを思う。俺たち三人の。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3187
translate jp a1c10o1_8ef5a995:

    # "I can see students walking back and forth through the courtyard, probably in preparation of their own projects."
    "中庭を生徒が行き交うのが見える。自分のところの企画の準備だろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3189
translate jp a1c10o1_bedba1a5:

    # "The festival is practically here. That means there are only two possible reasons that my help is required."
    "学園祭はもう始まったようなものだ。つまり、俺の手伝いが必要な理由は二つしかない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3191
translate jp a1c10o1_e404ecbd:

    # "Either there is only a small amount of work left, and they just want a helping hand to wrap up the mundane final checks they are obligated to do."
    "もうほとんど仕事なんて残ってなくて、単調な最終チェックを片付けるのを手伝ってほしいだけか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3193
translate jp a1c10o1_92865974:

    # "Or there is a ton of work left, and Shizune is putting on a calm face as a torrent of built-up procrastinated work threatens to kill us all."
    "実はまだ仕事が山ほど残っていて、先延ばし続けて積み上がった作業が土石流みたいに俺たち全員を飲み込もうとしているのに、静音は平気なふりをしているだけか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3200
translate jp a1c10o2_785258ea:

    # "Even so, they have really crossed the line this time. Nosy annoyances."
    "とうとう、こいつらは最後の一線を越えた。邪魔くさい奴らだ。いちいち首をつっこみやがって。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3202
translate jp a1c10o2_ca0a164b:

    # hi "It's nothing."
    hi "なんでもない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3207
translate jp a1c10o2_c8e43eaa:

    # mi "Really~, Hicchan? It doesn't look like it's nothing to me."
    mi "ほんとに～、ひっちゃん？　なんでもないようには見えないけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3212
translate jp a1c10o2_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3217
translate jp a1c10o2_e0551b9a:

    # mi "What a long line of bottles, right~? Right~! What are all of those, Hicchan?"
    mi "ビンがたくさんだよね～？　ね～！　そんなにいっぱいなんなの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3219
translate jp a1c10o2_dabe5b77:

    # hi "Just a few things."
    hi "ちょっとな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3224
translate jp a1c10o2_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3229
translate jp a1c10o2_e74f65ba:

    # mi "That looks like a lot more than 'just a few things'…"
    mi "『ちょっと』っていうには多すぎるんじゃないかな……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3231
translate jp a1c10o2_0d31ecdf:

    # "I can't fault either of them for being this way. Misha's just talking for Shizune, and Shizune is just curious by nature. Still, I wish the two of them would stop digging and take the hint. But Misha wouldn't pick up on it, and Shizune can't."
    "二人がそうやって詮索するのを責めることはできない。ミーシャは静音のかわりにしゃべってるだけだし、静音はもとから好奇心が強い。 それでも俺はこれ以上二人にかぎ回られたくないし、そろそろ察して欲しい。でもミーシャは気づかないし、静音は気づくことができない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3233
translate jp a1c10o2_489868e2:

    # "Because of that, they keep pressing on."
    "だから二人は詮索をやめない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3235
translate jp a1c10o2_3c24c150:

    # hi "It's really none of your business."
    hi "お前らには関係ないだろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3237
translate jp a1c10o2_760e76a5:

    # hi "Shouldn't you be leaving? A man's room is private, you know."
    hi "そろそろ出たらどうなんだ？　人の部屋なんだから。プライベートだろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3239
translate jp a1c10o2_2572b3fd:

    # "Shizune seems to take that as a challenge."
    "静音はそれを挑戦と受け取ったようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3244
translate jp a1c10o2_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3249
translate jp a1c10o2_e2f28253:

    # mi "What does that mean, Hicchan? When someone sees something interesting, their first instinct is to ask what it is, that's obvious. What's wrong with that?"
    mi "それどういう意味、ひっちゃん？　興味を引くものを見かけたら、それが何か聞くのは本能ってものよ。当たり前じゃない。何が悪いっていうの？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3251
translate jp a1c10o2_eccabcee:

    # hi "Because, like I said, there's nothing to see."
    hi "さっきも言っただろ。見るものなんて何もないんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3256
translate jp a1c10o2_e542b358:

    # mi "Hicchan, I think Shicchan is just concerned."
    mi "ひっちゃん、しっちゃんは心配してるだけだと思うよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3258
translate jp a1c10o2_7138a90f:

    # hi "What I have in my room isn't any of your business, that's all."
    hi "俺の部屋にあるものはお前らには関係ない。それだけだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3263
translate jp a1c10o2_e237d739:

    # mi "But…"
    mi "でも……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3265
translate jp a1c10o2_57c1af50:

    # hi "Damn it! Sometimes, I wish you two would just stop playing around so much. It's not funny all the time. You know that, right?"
    hi "ちくしょう！　お前らふざけるのもいいかげんにしろよ。それが面白くないときだってあるんだよ。そのくらいわかるだろ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3267
translate jp a1c10o2_4cc14bf8:

    # "I say it way more strongly than I meant to, almost yelling straight at Misha's face. She flinches and freezes in mid-sign, and even Shizune reacts to it even though she didn't hear me."
    "思っていたより強く言いすぎてしまい、ほとんどミーシャの顔に向けて怒鳴りつけていた。ミーシャは驚いて手話の途中で止まってしまう。聞こえないはずの静音まで反応している。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3271
translate jp a1c10o2_e44bcb5c:

    # "I guess my angry face said all that needs to be said to her."
    "俺の怒りの表情から、言いたいことは全部伝わったようだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3277
translate jp a1c10o2_ee1fa8af:

    # "After Misha slowly finishes the translation, the girls look at each other regretfully."
    "ミーシャがゆっくりと訳し終えると、二人は悔やむようにお互いを見あう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3282
translate jp a1c10o2_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3284
translate jp a1c10o2_f824053b:

    # mi "Okay, Hicchan, we'll leave you alone."
    mi "わかったよ、ひっちゃん。わたしたち行くね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3286
translate jp a1c10o2_61a0dcc4:

    # "It's the first time I've heard Misha speak without that familiar lilting up-and-down quality in her voice. It feels so strange to hear, and I want to apologize, but they have already turned to leave."
    "俺は初めて、あの陽気で上がり下がりの激しい調子抜きでミーシャが話すのを耳にする。ひどく奇妙な感じがする。俺は謝りたかったけど、二人はもう背を向けて部屋を出ている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3288
translate jp a1c10o2_a67a8a33:

    # "As the silence settles in, I regret what I said more and more."
    "静寂が訪れるとともに、俺はますます今の言葉を後悔する。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3294
translate jp a1c10o2_6ef45d07:

    # "The girls leave quietly, and after a while of standing in my room I dress up and follow after them."
    "二人は静かに部屋を出て行く。俺はしばらく立ちつくしていたけど、服を着てその後に続く。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3301
translate jp a1c11o1_7eef3fbc:

    # "God damn it. She just doesn't know when to stop."
    "ちくしょう。いい加減にしろってんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3303
translate jp a1c11o1_63120938:

    # hi "Yeah fine. Whatever. I'll tell you. I was having a great time."
    hi "ああそうかよ。わかった。教えてやる。すげえ楽しかったさ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3305
translate jp a1c11o1_dd713f8d:

    # hi "I had a heart attack first thing in the morning and then hung out with the head nurse for a few hours for kicks."
    hi "今日朝イチで心臓発作起こして、何時間もナースと一緒にお楽しみだったんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3307
translate jp a1c11o1_3d2297b2:

    # hi "Best morning of my life, I gotta tell you."
    hi "人生最高の朝だぜ。マジで"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3309
translate jp a1c11o1_a94df063:

    # "I'm trying to imitate her ridiculous lilting speech while keeping my voice so low that nobody else hears me. The words come spitting out of my mouth."
    "ミーシャのバカみたいに陽気な口調を真似してみるけど、周りに聞こえないよう小さな声でしゃべる。その言葉ははき出すような調子になる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3314
translate jp a1c11o1_6d42f748:

    # mi "Hicchan, you had a what? Seriously?"
    mi "なにそれ、ひっちゃん？　本当なの？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3316
translate jp a1c11o1_ed91a490:

    # hi "Just drop it. You heard me."
    hi "これ以上聞くなよ。聞こえただろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3321
translate jp a1c11o1_15c36dcb:

    # mi "But Hicchan, this is important!"
    mi "でもひっちゃん、これ大事なことでしょ！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3323
translate jp a1c11o1_553ea39c:

    # hi "No, really. Leave me alone. We're in the middle of the class, too."
    hi "だめだ。いいからほっとけよ。それに今は授業中だろ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3328
translate jp a1c11o1_2d6771d2:

    # mi "But Hicchan!"
    mi "でもひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3330
translate jp a1c11o1_bb8181c3:

    # "Misha sounds concerned, or maybe panicky. I wonder if she realizes herself that it wasn't the best of ideas to be so damn intrusive."
    "ミーシャは心配してるようだ。パニック状態かもしれない。そうやって首突っ込まれるのが嫌なんだってこと、気づいてないのか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3332
translate jp a1c11o1_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3334
translate jp a1c11o1_048997cf:

    # "I let her simmer in her own juices for a while before replying. It won't translate to Shizune but I don't care."
    "しばらく自分がしでかしたことを思い知らせてから、俺は答えてやる。静音には伝わらないだろうけど、知ったことか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3336
translate jp a1c11o1_4767f624:

    # hi "Piss off, Misha."
    hi "お前ウザいんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3338
translate jp a1c11o1_2e16517e:

    # hi "And tell Shizune to do so too."
    hi "静音にもそう言ってやれ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3340
translate jp a1c11o1_81b01b88:

    # "As the words leave my mouth, I immediately regret saying them, but it's not like I can take them back any more."
    "そう口にした直後に後悔するけど、でも言ったことはもう取り消せない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3351
translate jp a1c11o1_3dcff7d9:

    # "To my partial surprise, Misha actually shuts up though I don't bother checking if she passes the message to Shizune. Doesn't matter either way."
    "ミーシャは本当に口をつぐんだので、俺は少し驚く。でも静音に通訳したかどうかは確かめない。してもしなくても関係ない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3353
translate jp a1c11o1_26985e86:

    # "Mutou ends his class in some generic talk about the festival two days from now."
    "武藤先生は二日後の学園祭についてどうでもいい話をして、授業を終える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3358
translate jp a1c11o2_29ce1e3c:

    # hi "Give up. I'm not going to tell."
    hi "あきらめろよ。絶対言わないからな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3363
translate jp a1c11o2_2489eb65:

    # mi "Is that so~?"
    mi "そーなの～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3365
translate jp a1c11o2_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3370
translate jp a1c11o2_5032d6d4:

    # "She thinks about this for a moment."
    "ミーシャはしばらく考える。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3375
translate jp a1c11o2_bf9fa71b:

    # mi "That's stingy, Hicchan~!"
    mi "けちだよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3377
translate jp a1c11o2_3426e2af:

    # "I can hear the pout in her voice, disappointed and downcast."
    "不機嫌さが声ににじみ出ている。いかにも失望したって感じだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3383
translate jp a1c11o2_0d084204:

    # "She retreats again for a moment to negotiate with the brainy half of the dynamic duo, before returning."
    "またしばらく引き下がって、パワフルコンビの頭のいいほうに相談してから戻ってくる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3390
translate jp a1c11o2_5c19b9aa:

    # mi "I think we should have lunch together and discuss more about this… Shicchan says."
    mi "一緒にお昼食べながら話を聞きましょうか……ってしっちゃんが言ってる"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3395
translate jp a1c11o2_2c88b13f:

    # mi "It's our treat."
    mi "わたしたちのおごりだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3400
translate jp a1c11o2_89934dc6:

    # mi "Besides, you need to make up for not being there in the morning and we need help with the work~!"
    mi "それに、今朝わたしたちが手伝ってほしかったのにひっちゃんはいなかったんだから、埋め合わせしてもらわなくちゃね～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3402
translate jp a1c11o2_4f6d6ee3:

    # "The other students around us are starting to give us looks, probably because Misha is leaning so much over her desk that she's almost bumping heads with me. Her curly hair brushes my neck."
    "他の生徒たちがこっちを見はじめてる。ミーシャが机から思い切り身を乗り出して、俺に頭をこすりつけてきてるからだろう。ミーシャの巻き毛が俺の首筋に触れる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3404
translate jp a1c11o2_496f5418:

    # "It smells like shampoo and very much like whatever she puts in there to make it go like that."
    "シャンプーと、髪をセットするために使っているんだろう、何かの香りがする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3406
translate jp a1c11o2_c1e80373:

    # "I think the girl in front of me is trying to eavesdrop. Hope nobody is getting the wrong idea about this, though I'm not really sure how it would be possible to get any other kind of idea."
    "前の席の女子が聞き耳を立ててるようだ。誰も勘違いしてくれなきゃいいけど、でもこんな状況で勘違いせずにいてくれる人がいるか、自信がない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3408
translate jp a1c11o2_7f37e25c:

    # "Luckily Mutou stays oblivious, or deliberately ignores Misha. So far."
    "幸運なことに武藤先生は気づいていない。あるいはミーシャをわざと無視しているのか。今のところは。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3410
translate jp a1c11o2_ff608d1c:

    # "I can't really win this one, can I?"
    "これは逃げるのは無理だよ、なあ？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3431
translate jp a1c12o1_3ff34924:

    # hi "Sorry, I can't. I promised to have lunch with someone else already."
    hi "悪い、行けないんだ。もう他の人と昼を食べるって約束してて"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3436
translate jp a1c12o1_daf35118:

    # mi "Eeeh? Who? Is it a girl~?"
    mi "ええぇ？　誰なの？　女の子～？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3438
translate jp a1c12o1_200e7fb1:

    # hi "Yeah…"
    hi "ああ……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3443
translate jp a1c12o1_54d0c987:

    # "Her giggle compels me to quickly follow with something so she doesn't get the wrong idea."
    "ミーシャのくすくす笑いに、勘違いされないようあわててフォローを入れる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3445
translate jp a1c12o1_320046a8:

    # hi "It's nothing like that! It's… a bit complicated."
    hi "そういうのじゃないぞ！　ちょっと……複雑な事情なんだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3450
translate jp a1c12o1_a0cd392f:

    # "Complicated… yeah, that's what my life is, despite already setting into a daily routine of school life."
    "複雑……そうだ、それが俺の人生だ。もう学校生活という日常に落ち着き始めてはいても。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3452
translate jp a1c12o1_cba8e94f:

    # "All things must be put into a new kind of perspective in this second life, reconsidered from the point of view of this new me."
    "この第二の人生、すべてを新しい角度で見ないとダメだ。これからの俺の視点から見直した価値観で。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3454
translate jp a1c12o1_0f98fce0:

    # "The me with a broken heart."
    "心臓のぶっ壊れた、この俺の。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3456
translate jp a1c12o1_e2fc226c:

    # hi "Also, I don't know if I can come to the council after all."
    hi "あと、やっぱり生徒会には顔出せないかもしれない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3458
translate jp a1c12o1_ff0befdc:

    # hi "Or at least for now. I have something else I need to focus on first."
    hi "少なくとも今は。他に集中しなきゃいけないことがあるんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3460
translate jp a1c12o1_484646c7:

    # "That's right. I have to rethink my priorities. This is something that has swirled around in my head since the nurse gave me that speech. I really can't afford to pretend I don't have this condition."
    "そうだ。何をして何をしないか、俺は優先順位を考え直さないと。ナースに説教されてから、そのことがずっと頭の中でぐるぐる回っていた。自分が病気じゃないふりをするなんて、そんな余裕は俺にはない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3462
translate jp a1c12o1_5f00125c:

    # "I'm surprised that I can think so analytically, but I'll go with the flow for now."
    "こんなに自分が分析的に考えられることに、自分でも驚く。でも今はこの流れに身を任せることにする。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3464
translate jp a1c12o1_7e364d0e:

    # hi "I promise I'll explain properly later, but not now, okay? Please tell Shizune I'm sorry for letting her down."
    hi "後でちゃんと説明するって、約束する。でも今は待ってくれ、な？　がっかりさせてごめんって静音にも伝えてほしい"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3469
translate jp a1c12o1_f6044364:

    # mi "If you say so, Hicchan."
    mi "うん、わかったよ、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3471
translate jp a1c12o1_c85d32cd:

    # "She sounds surprised, and serious, which I don't think I've ever heard Misha to be before."
    "ミーシャは驚いたようだ。そして真剣だった。今までこんな話し方をするのは聞いたことがない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3481
translate jp a1c12o1_0afb3bef:

    # "Misha luckily understands that I'm serious, a stroke of luck that I could tell what I mean so clearly even she got it. She retreats to translate our discussion to Shizune."
    "幸い、ミーシャは俺が真剣だと理解してくれた。ミーシャにすらちゃんと俺の意図が伝わった、というのは思いがけない幸運だ。そのまま引き下がり、ミーシャは静音に話の内容を通訳する。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3483
translate jp a1c12o1_9a594a66:

    # "Neither of them talk to me after that."
    "その後は二人とも俺には話しかけてこない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3490
translate jp a1c12o2_1d5739fc:

    # hi "Fine, I'll come with you, but get off my back for the rest of the class, okay?"
    hi "わかった、一緒に行くよ。でも授業が終わるまでは離れててくれないか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3495
translate jp a1c12o2_76c7269d:

    # mi "It's a deal, Hicchan~!"
    mi "いいよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3516
translate jp a1c12o2_865e5fc9:

    # "On the way to the student council room, I can see students walking back and forth through the halls, probably in preparation of their own projects."
    "生徒会室に行く途中、廊下を行き交う生徒をたくさん見かける。たぶん自分の企画の準備をしているんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3518
translate jp a1c12o2_bedba1a5:

    # "The festival is practically here. That means there are only two possible reasons that my help is required."
    "学園祭はもう始まったようなものだ。つまり、俺の手伝いが必要な理由は二つしかない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3520
translate jp a1c12o2_e404ecbd:

    # "Either there is only a small amount of work left, and they just want a helping hand to wrap up the mundane final checks they are obligated to do."
    "もうほとんど仕事なんて残ってなくて、単調な最終チェックを片付けるのを手伝ってほしいだけか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3522
translate jp a1c12o2_92865974:

    # "Or there is a ton of work left, and Shizune is putting on a calm face as a torrent of built-up procrastinated work threatens to kill us all."
    "実はまだ仕事が山ほど残っていて、先延ばし続けて積み上がった作業が土石流みたいに俺たち全員を飲み込もうとしているのに、静音は平気なふりをしているだけか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3531
translate jp a1c13o1_e1a21bb4:

    # hi "It's all right, I just need to catch my breath. My condition isn't the best, these days."
    hi "ちょっと一休みすれば大丈夫だから。最近、体調が良くなくて"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3536
translate jp a1c13o1_a22243e5:

    # li "Oh."
    li "まあ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3538
translate jp a1c13o1_2d0cbe2c:

    # li "Is it something that… is related to you being transferred here? I mean…"
    li "それは……ここに転校して来たことと何か関係があるんですか？　つまり……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3543
translate jp a1c13o1_7cd644ee:

    # "She cuts herself off rather abruptly, maybe realizing she was being a bit intrusive. Her instincts are sharp though, and while I don't like the subject it's not like I should lie about it."
    "リリーは不意に言葉を切る。たぶん、少し踏み込みすぎたと気づいたんだ。それにしても彼女の勘は鋭い。俺はこのことを話したくはないけど、わざわざ嘘をつくほどでもない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3545
translate jp a1c13o1_38c8c95e:

    # "If it's Lilly, I don't think I mind."
    "リリーになら、俺は気にしない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3547
translate jp a1c13o1_743d3b3d:

    # hi "I'm just a little weak for the time being."
    hi "最近、ちょっと体が弱っててさ。それだけだよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3552
translate jp a1c13o1_49b9c918:

    # li "Hanako said you look fairly… healthy, so I naturally thought…"
    li "華ちゃんが、久夫さんは割と……健康そうに見えると言っていたので、私もそうなのかと思って……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3557
translate jp a1c13o1_706ac117:

    # "Lilly doesn't finish her sentence again, letting it trail off with a measure of concern."
    "心配そうな口調のまま、リリーの言葉はまたしても尻すぼみになる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3559
translate jp a1c13o1_48c64d88:

    # "As she furrows her brow, Lilly's uncomfortable expression spurs me to say at least something to ease her feelings."
    "眉をよせたリリーの不安そうな表情を見て、気持ちが焦る。せめて何か気を楽にしてやれることを言わないと。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3561
translate jp a1c13o1_9d63c571:

    # "It's surprising she's this flustered, considering her straightforward attitude with her own blindness. She must know that not all share her own comfort about such things."
    "リリーの目の障害に対する率直な姿勢を考えると、この狼狽ぶりは驚きだ。みんながリリーと同じように障害と向き合えるわけじゃないってことはわかっているはずなのに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3563
translate jp a1c13o1_9c896a09:

    # hi "No, it's okay."
    hi "いや、いいんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3565
translate jp a1c13o1_db33031a:

    # hi "I have a pretty… I guess the best way to put it would be messed-up… heart. Arrhythmia."
    hi "俺、心臓が……壊れてる、っていうのが一番近いかな。不整脈なんだ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3567
translate jp a1c13o1_20159f35:

    # hi "I had a bad heart attack a while ago because of it, and spent most of the spring in a hospital. Ended in Yamaku on doctor's orders."
    hi "そのせいで、しばらく前にきつい心臓の発作があったんだよ。春の間はほとんど病院で過ごして、医者の指示で山久学園に、ってわけさ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3569
translate jp a1c13o1_3bf8d73f:

    # "She silently nods her head in acknowledgment."
    "リリーはそれを聞いて、静かにうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3571
translate jp a1c13o1_95679c8a:

    # "My answer, though, only seems to make Lilly furrow her brow even further. She doesn't seem to quite know how to react, given we don't really know each other that well."
    "でも、俺の答えにリリーはますます眉を寄せる。そこまで互いを知っているわけではないから、どう反応していいのかわからないんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3573
translate jp a1c13o1_6cc5e64f:

    # "I can't really fault her for it, given I have the exact same reaction."
    "俺の立場だって全く同じだ。リリーを責めることはできない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3576
translate jp a1c13o1_927dd8c7:

    # "To my surprise, in a moment's time her face shows that she comes to some sort of realization."
    "驚いたことに、リリーはすぐに何かに思い当たったような表情を浮かべる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3581
translate jp a1c13o1_ddfdfec9:

    # li "Wait… so the time when Emi and you collided in the hallway…?"
    li "待ってください……その、笑美さんと廊下でぶつかった時も……？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3583
translate jp a1c13o1_e4542979:

    # "I grimace slightly. Her ability to connect the dots quite so fast is unexpected."
    "俺はわずかに顔をしかめる。次から次へと点を結ぶリリーの能力は思ってもみないほど素早かった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3585
translate jp a1c13o1_85b62ae0:

    # hi "Yeah. I guess I'm a textbook example of why those rules about running in the corridors exist."
    hi "ああ、廊下で走ってはいけないっていう校則がある理由のわかりやすいお手本だな"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3590
translate jp a1c13o1_538dfc28:

    # "That was a lot more dry than I'd intended. Lilly visibly shies away from continuing the topic."
    "思ったよりはるかにそっけない言い方だ。明らかにリリーはこの話を続けることをためらっている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3592
translate jp a1c13o1_61bd26be:

    # "While I do want to assuage her concern, I really don't want to dwell on this either."
    "リリーの心配を和らげてあげたいが、この話題を続けたくもない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3594
translate jp a1c13o1_6007b55c:

    # hi "Don't worry about it."
    hi "気にすんなって"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3599
translate jp a1c13o1_49849090:

    # "I try to offer a reassuring smile but then I realize the futility. Without knowing this, Lilly smiles at me reassuringly but doesn't say anything further."
    "笑顔を見せて元気づけようとするけど、意味がないと気づく。そうとも知らずに、リリーは俺を元気づけようと微笑みかけてくる。ただ、それ以上は何も言わない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3609
translate jp a1c13o1_54086bba:

    # "Arriving at the dorms, Rin stops in front of her mural as if lightning struck her. She had been so quiet for almost all of the walk back that I had all but forgotten she was here."
    "寮に到着すると、琳は自分の壁画の前で雷に打たれたように立ち止まる。帰り道ではほとんど黙っていたから、琳がここにいたことをもう少しで忘れるところだった。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3614
translate jp a1c13o1_d6e741b5:

    # rin "It's Friday, isn't it?"
    rin "今日って金曜だったよね？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3619
translate jp a1c13o1_46bb2e14:

    # li "Yes… Friday, the eighth of June."
    li "ええ……金曜ですよ。６月８日の"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3626
translate jp a1c13o1_2bd946fe:

    # rin "This is bad."
    rin "大変だ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3631
translate jp a1c13o1_d9332f6c:

    # li "Bad? Why?"
    li "大変？　どうしてですか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3636
translate jp a1c13o1_a627f624:

    # rin "I think I am going to go in a fetal position and throw up. Possibly in reverse order."
    rin "今すぐ膝を抱えて吐きそう。順番はもしかしたら逆だけど"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3641
translate jp a1c13o1_b5500cda:

    # li "Is something wrong?"
    li "何か問題でも？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3646
translate jp a1c13o1_15cea99c:

    # rin "No. Nothing is wrong. It's Friday and nothing is wrong yet. This mural, it's going to need to be finished by Sunday. So everything's all right."
    rin "いや、問題はないよ。今日は金曜だから、まだ問題ない。この絵、日曜までに完成させなきゃいけないの。だから何も問題ない"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3651
translate jp a1c13o1_88a4a358:

    # rin "Do you have any drugs? Or a time machine?"
    rin "クスリでも持ってない？　あるいはタイムマシーンとか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3656
translate jp a1c13o1_23fc9b9a:

    # rin "This is not good. Not good."
    rin "これはまずい。まずいよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3658
translate jp a1c13o1_87875f71:

    # "So she's behind her schedule. Recalling Shizune's exasperation at Rin's carefree attitude several days ago, I don't know what to think."
    "ということは、琳の予定は遅れているのか。数日前、のんきな態度の琳に静音が激怒していたのを思うと、どうなっているのやら。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3660
translate jp a1c13o1_0d3c23be:

    # "She has left herself open for a 'told you so' unless she can pull off whatever she needs to pull off by Sunday morning."
    "なんであれ、日曜の朝までにやるべき作業を終えることができなければ、琳は『だから言ったでしょ』となじられる運命にあるわけだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3662
translate jp a1c13o1_d1a47786:

    # "Rin keeps staring at her mural looking as mortified as she can."
    "琳は壁画を屈辱的に見つめ続ける。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3667
translate jp a1c13o1_5fa997b3:

    # rin "Leave me. I'm going to need to work for a while."
    rin "先に行って。少しでも進めなきゃ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3669
translate jp a1c13o1_a2ae5d7e:

    # "I glance at Lilly, expecting her to share an incredulous look with me as I roll my eyes, but then I realize she's not one to do that kind of thing."
    "俺はちらりとリリーを見る。俺と同じようにあきれ顔をしているだろうかと期待したけど、考えてみればリリーはそういうことをする子じゃない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3674
translate jp a1c13o1_1fb68b17:

    # rin "Leave me."
    rin "行って"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3685
translate jp a1c13o1_c42c5404:

    # "We do, of course, not wanting to aggravate her any more than she already is."
    "もちろん、俺たちはそうする。これ以上琳を刺激したくない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3687
translate jp a1c13o1_db8cb954:

    # "There is a churning bad feeling in my gut. Rin sure has a knack of making people feel worried about her."
    "腹の中をかき回されるような、嫌な予感がする。琳には間違いなく人を不安にさせる才能がある。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3689
translate jp a1c13o1_1f204f10:

    # "She seems like a person who should never be left alone."
    "琳を野放しにしてはいけないんじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3691
translate jp a1c13o1_69cd2c61:

    # hi "Maybe we should call someone? She sounded like she was going into shock or something."
    hi "誰かを呼んだほうがいいのかな？　ショック症か何か起こしそうだし"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3696
translate jp a1c13o1_c40d05b1:

    # li "I'm sure she will be just fine. She's just a… eeeh… how to say…"
    li "大丈夫だと思いますよ。彼女はその……ええと……何て言っていいか……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3698
translate jp a1c13o1_08d2b333:

    # "Lilly cocks her head a little, trying to find a polite way of calling Rin crazy without calling her crazy."
    "リリーは頭を少し傾け、琳がおかしいということを、『おかしい』という言葉を使わず礼儀正しく表現しようとしている。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3700
translate jp a1c13o1_490c372a:

    # hi "Unique?"
    hi "ユニークってこと？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3705
translate jp a1c13o1_01556dd2:

    # li "Yes, a very unique person."
    li "ええ、とてもユニークな人なんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3707
translate jp a1c13o1_112eaa6a:

    # hi "I guess you could say that."
    hi "それは言えてると思うよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3712
translate jp a1c13o1_41a1dbe0:

    # "She giggles at the notion melodiously, nodding in agreement."
    "リリーはその意見にクスクスと笑い、納得してうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3717
translate jp a1c13o1_6b84c1b0:

    # li "Sorry about leaving you stranded as you talked to her. I… don't really understand her, so I keep my distance."
    li "あなたが琳さんと話している間、知らないふりをしてすみません。私……彼女のことは本当にわからないので、距離を置くようにしているんです"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3719
translate jp a1c13o1_03726f31:

    # "So my guess was right. Lilly offers a slight, apologetic smile as if she was sorry that her own shortcomings have prevented her from becoming closer to Rin."
    "思ったとおりだ。琳を敬遠してしまった自分の短所を謝るように、リリーは申し訳なさそうな笑顔をわずかに見せる。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3721
translate jp a1c13o1_08de51d9:

    # "I'm not one to blame her. At all."
    "決してリリーを責めることはできない。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3723
translate jp a1c13o1_b3cef877:

    # "Lilly lets slip a long breath, probably a disguised yawn. I imagine she's as exhausted by all this as I am."
    "リリーは深く息をもらす。きっと欠伸をごまかしたんだろう。俺と同じように、今日の出来事に疲れたんだと思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3728
translate jp a1c13o1_ac7b29c3:

    # li "I'd better leave now and give these to Hanako. Thank you for the company, Hisao."
    li "華ちゃんにこれを渡さないといけないので、私はもう行きますね。一緒にいてくれてありがとう、久夫さん"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3730
translate jp a1c13o1_75ab13a0:

    # "She smiles very sweetly at me. It feels different than normal, despite the fact that she seems to be smiling so often."
    "リリーは俺に愛らしく微笑む。いつもと違った感じがする。彼女はよく微笑んでいるのに。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3732
translate jp a1c13o1_85e6f648:

    # "I can't put my finger on what the difference is. It's just different."
    "その違いがなんなのかなんてわからない。ただ違っていたんだ。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3734
translate jp a1c13o1_c2f28808:

    # "Relaxed, I'd say, but that's probably just relief over getting rid of Rin. Maybe."
    "ゆったりしていた、とでも言えばいいのか。でもそれは、単に琳から逃れた開放感のせいだろう。たぶん。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3736
translate jp a1c13o1_386edd70:

    # hi "Yeah… good night. Say hi to Hanako for me."
    hi "うん……おやすみ。華子によろしく言っておいて"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3741
translate jp a1c13o1_731745b4:

    # li "I will. Good night."
    li "ええ。おやすみなさい"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3757
translate jp a1c13o2_3aca8c5c:

    # hi "I… I'm fine."
    hi "だ……大丈夫だよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3759
translate jp a1c13o2_fcaebb6f:

    # hi "There's nothing to worry about, the hill is just surprisingly steep, don't you think?"
    hi "心配することなんてないよ。この丘がびっくりするほど急なだけで。そう思わないか？"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3761
translate jp a1c13o2_68b71462:

    # hi "I wonder what they have the school so high up here for anyway, don't we have students in wheelchairs and everything?"
    hi "いったいなんでこんな高い所に学校を建てたのかな？　車椅子の生徒とかいるのに"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3766
translate jp a1c13o2_499574f0:

    # li "Indeed."
    li "そうですね"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3771
translate jp a1c13o2_b7dbaf9f:

    # "Lilly's forehead wrinkles in concern, and I don't really want her to have that kind of an expression over me. We barely know each other."
    "リリーの額に気遣いがしわになって浮かぶ。俺のことでリリーにこんな表情なんてして欲しくなかった。俺たちはほとんど知りあってもいないじゃないか。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3773
translate jp a1c13o2_6b6c3c88:

    # hi "Yeah, my thoughts exactly. Not that you can find a place like this wherever, I guess, but it makes me wonder what they were thinking."
    hi "な、そう思うだろ。こういう場所はどこにでもあるわけじゃないのにさ。なんでわざわざここを選んだのか不思議だよ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3775
translate jp a1c13o2_35d15dbc:

    # "My voice is overly calm, it sounds weird to my own ear and I speak way too fast. I briefly wonder how much Lilly can sense from someone's voice alone."
    "俺の声は軽薄なまでに穏やかだ。俺自身の耳にも奇妙に響くし、しゃべるのが早口すぎる。リリーは人の声を聞くだけで、どれだけのことを感じ取れるんだろう、と思う。"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3777
translate jp a1c13o2_dbf4e823:

    # li "Mmm…"
    li "でも……"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3779
translate jp a1c13o2_90085da8:

    # hi "Let's continue. We're almost there anyway."
    hi "さ、行こう。もうすぐ山久だ"

# game/script-a1-friday.rpy:3785
translate jp a1c13o2_682226a1:

    # "For the rest of the way back to the school, we all remain silent."
    "学校までの道のりの間、俺たちは三人ともずっと無言のままだった。"

